\id 1KI - Ekajuk Bible 
\h 1Atul 
\toc1 Ngbokambanga Nwer nyi Atul 
\toc2 1 Atul 
\toc3 1 Atu 
\mt1 Atu/ 
\c 1  
\s1 Ngare Nyi Devid Ma Kul 
\p  
\v 1 Ngare nyi Devid ma sahb kˈkul, jol afi bo konng-e egbvgbv ebbik ebbik, á joom tiki bel elfuubu.  
\v 2 Alokeltum ebe kehm-e tongo re, <<Nong wahr seb mongunga nnenkal, no bahke jo loko ntul, fere jo kpur-e. Á bahke ma noongo go egea nkpe, eji nso ntul ewahre bahke bele elfuubu.>> 
\p  
\v 3 Owo bo kehm yannge seb nnobo noba mmonse nkal go Isreel kpee, kehm song nyehn Abisagi, nne ejahbe Sunam, kehm-e koko ba ka ntul.  
\v 4 Mmonse nkal jolo nne ano; á jo kpuru ntul, jo lok-e, wo ntul tikem noongo a ne. 
\s1 Adonija Sebe Re Á Ko Eti Etul 
\p  
\v 5 Ngare nyia, Adonija, ye ji bo jo lung nnyehn re Hagiti, kehm mehle elne wahre, kehm bungu re, <<M bahke jolo ntul.>> Ano wo á kehm toobo amvtv akuungu a anyꞌnya, a ane atahl abal ane awubu ba bahke jo gbo-e mbang.  
\v 6 <<Jol nde we-e ka nyˈnyam, fere bahb-e re, <<Jenji wahnge a kpꞌlimi eljini nia?>> Adonija jolo nne ano, ye wo bo jele kunu Absalom.>> 
\p  
\v 7 Adonija kpa njahm a Joab ji mmona Jeruya, a Abiata ji nlimajom, bo kun-e abo go njahm  
\v 8 Wo Jadok ji nlimajom, Benaya mmona Jehoiada, Natan ji nnyehnamahr, Simeyi a Reyi, a akahme kahme ane ba jo baabe Devid taamem semme elbo a ntoobo nyi Adonija.  
\v 9 Adonija kehm koko ejoro, adahmagbudu a ajoko joko abon efong song lim ajom go Eltal ni Joheleti kohlo En Rogel. Á tiingi abonanyehn kpee, ba li abon ntul, a aneblum ba Juda kpee ba kpo lim eltum etahk ntul,  
\v 10 wo á tiingem Natan ji nnyehnamahr, afi Benaya, afi akahme kahme ane ba jo baabe ntul, afi Solomon ji mmonannyehn. 
\p  
\v 11 Owo Natan kehm bahbe Batiseba ji nnyehn Solomon re, <<Á ka wuk re Adonija, ji mmona Hagiti, ebjol ntul, jol nsoo ntula Devid kahnema?  
\v 12 Anv nong me n tub-a elle, ana á bahke tahre elkpin ena, a ni Solomon mmon ewa.  
\v 13 Song go ekpˈkpa goji Ntula Devid, song tong-e re, <<Nsoo ntul, á tirem tong me nlokeltum ewa re, <<Etingitingi Solomon mmon ewa wo bahke jolo ntul toon-ma?, ye wo bahke jehke go egame eti etula? ˈNꞌnan wahnge Adonija ma fere jol ntul?>>  
\v 14 Ana a kpi mbungu mbungu a ntul, m bahke bake ba kpir-a o, ba tong ntul re, ji a kpꞌbungu lohko li ano.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Ano wo Betiseba mehle song nyehn ntul no ma sahb kˈkul go ege ekpꞌkpa, eji Abisagi nnea Sunem jo kpur-e.  
\v 16 Betiseba kehm gongo noongo go ndi, go esamahr ntul. 
\p Ntul kehm-e bahbe re, <<Jenji á kpꞌsebe?>> 
\p  
\v 17 Á kehm faange ntul re, <<Ntul ewame, wofono antahng wo tiri tong-m me nlokeltum ewa go mbing nyi Jehova Esowo eba re, <<Solomon mmon ewa wo bahke jolo ntul toon-m, ye wo bahke jehke go egame eti etul.>>  
\v 18 Wo anv, Adonija wo ma jol ntul, nga wo ntul ewame, wo ka kahn bade.  
\v 19 Adonija eblim ajom, ko ajoko joko abon efong gbalee, a adahmagbudu, ejoro, fere tiingi abon ntul, Abiata ji nlimajom a Joab ji ntubesia nsoja, wo Solomon nlokeltum ewa, á we-e tiingem.  
\v 20 Nsoo ntul ewame, amahr nya anebe Isreel kpee kpi wo seenge, re bo kahn go ega nne no bahke jehke go eti etul ji nso ntul toon-e.  
\v 21 A tohko lim ano, ana bo kpꞌkpake babnso ewahne kak elahm a babnde ebo, me a Solomon mmon ewame, bo bahk-r jabbe ana abi ane.>> 
\p  
\v 22 Ana á kpi mbungu mbungu a ntul, nyehn Natan ji nnyehnamahr ma ba lohng.  
\v 23 Bo kehm tongo ntul re, <<Natan ji nnyehamahr li a.>> Á kehm tahme go esamahr ntul, kehm song gong esamahr ebe go ndi. 
\p  
\v 24 Natan kehm bungu tong ntul re, <<Nsoo ntul ewame, wobbung re, Adonija wo bahke jolo ntul no bahke jehke toon-aa? ye wo bahke jehke go ega eti etula?  
\v 25 Lela yeblohng song lim ajom, ko ajoko joko abon efong gbalee, efong, a ejoro. Yebtiingi abon ntul, fere tiingi atubesi asoja, a Abiata ji nlimanjom. Anv, bo baa go kpꞌlehke fere wꞌwo a ne, fere kpꞌbungu re, <<Nong elkpin ena lab, ntula Adonija!>>  
\v 26 Wo me, nlokeltum ewa, a Jadok nlimanjom, a Benaya mmon no Jehoida, go Solomon nlokeltum ewa, á wahr tiingem.  
\v 27 Ejum ji a ji nso ntul ewame ma lim, á sebem re wahr alokeltum eba kahn nne no bahke jehke go eti etul ji nso ntul ewahre toon-ea?>> 
\s1 Devid bobo Solomon Etul 
\p  
\v 28 Owo ntula Devid kehm bungu re, <<Lung Betiseba kam.>>Ejum ji nso ntul ewame ma lim ji a, á sebem re Ano wo á lohngo ba yiimi go esamahr ntul. 
\p  
\v 29 Owo ntul kehm koko nwongo re, <<Go etingitingi ana Jehova li go elkpin, ye ji ma-m tahre go ajoobo atongtong anyehng anyehng,  
\v 30 m bahke lohko lim lela go etingitingi ji n ko nwongo tong-a go esamahr bi Jehova Esowo bi Isreel. Solomon mmon ewa bahke jehke etul toon-m, á bahke jehke go egame eti etul, go egama enyo.>> Owo Betiseba kehm gongo esamahr ebe go ndi, fere noongo tanne go esamahr ntul, kehm bungu re, <<Nong nsoo ewame, ntula Devid bel nlabe elkpin!>> 
\p  
\v 31 Owo Betiseba kehm gongo esamahr ebe go ndi, fere noongo tanne go esamahr ntul, kehm bungu re, <<Nong nsoo ewame, ntula Devid bel nlabe elkpin!>> 
\p  
\v 32 Ntula Devid kehm bungu re, <<Lung Jadok ji nlimanjom, Natan ji nnyehnamahr, a Benaya mmona Jehoida kam.>> Eji bo ba no go esamahr bi ntul,  
\v 33 á kehm tongo bo re, "Roden nlokeltuma ntul wahn song, fere rod Solomon mmon ewame kunu go egame enyꞌnya ji kahbe akpade, song a ne go Gihon.  
\v 34 Nong Jadok ji nlimajom abola Natan ji nnyehnamahr, bo wohng-e akehng go edi jio, bob-r etul bi Isreel. Wor ntang, fere rabe re, <<Ntula Solomon, elkpin ena laboo!>>  
\v 35 Owo ḿ bahke tahme a ne, á song ji go egame eti etul, jo fili edi go egame enyo. M me-e yehke re á jol nfiladi go Isreel a Juda.> 
\p  
\v 36 Benaya mmona Jehoida kehm faange ntul re, <<Nong jol ano! Nong Jehova, Esowo bi nso ntul ewame bung yiimi tˈtahne.  
\v 37 Ana Jehova jolo a nsoo ntul ewame, nong á tob jol a Solomon, lim etul ebe gbal sehnge eti etul ji nso ntula David! 
\p  
\v 38 Ano wo Jadok ji nlimajom, Natan nnyehnamahr, go Benaya mmona Jehoida, anebe Kereti a anebe Peleti, bo mehle tahm, song rod Solomon kunu go enyꞌnya ji ntula Devid ji kahbe akpade, fere tv-e ko-e song rehng go Gihon.  
\v 39 Jadok ji nlimajom kehm rodo ntang nyi akehng wob atahng go mmobkpatahk no li saang ba kak Solomon akehng go esi. Owo bo kehm woro ntang, fvfo ane kpee kehm rabe re, <<Ntula Solomon, elkpin ena laboo!>>  
\v 40 Ane kpee kehm mehle tahm jo toon-e, jo wor agbehle, jo bel eyebatahng gbalee, ndi jo gbꞌgbehke go ewahl ji jo lim. 
\p  
\v 41 Adonija, a ajenne kpee nya jolo a ne wuku ewahl eji bo yahke li elkak ebo mal. Ana bo kpꞌwuku atang nya bo kpꞌworo, Joab kehm bahbe re, <<Elkohn ewahl ajii li go atahng ejahbe me?>>  
\v 42 Jol ana á kpi mbungu mbungu, Jonatan mmona Abiata ji nlimajom ebba lohng. Adonija kehm bungu re, <<Ba yel. Nnooba nne ana wo tiki kpi nnoobo etib.>>  
\v 43 Jonatan kehm faange re, <<Eꞌeeo! nsoo ntul ewahre Devid ebbob Solomon ntul.  
\v 44 Ntul me-e tum a Jadok ji nlimajom, Natan nnyehnamahr, Benaya mmon no Jehoida, anebe Kereti, anebe Peleti, fvfo bo me-e rod kunu go enyꞌnya ji ntul ji kahbe akpade,  
\v 45 fvfo Jadok ji nlimajom a Natan nnyehnamahr me-e bob etul go Gihon. Go wo bo lohngo no ba, ba yel go nfam, a ewahl ewahl ana bo ba no. Ewok ji o ji á kpꞌwuku.  
\v 46 Go nsol kpee, Solomon ebji go nji etul enye ana ntul.  
\v 47 Fvfo, ane ba kpo lim eltum a ntul, ebba kak nsoo ntula Devid nnyo re, <<Nong Esowo eba lim mbing nyi Solomon ga gbal sehnge nyꞌnya, nji etul enye bel ellub sehnge nyꞌnya!> Ntul gbo kohk esi eje go edilnong kak Esowo,  
\v 48 fere bung re, <Eltehke jol ka Jehova Esowo bi Isreel, ye ji ma wahng re me nyehn nne no bahke jehke toon-m go eti etul lela.> >>  
\v 49 Eji bo wuku jia, ajenne kpee nya ba goji Adonija mehle a elfahle, fere be raade no nne tahm mbang enye.  
\v 50 Wo Adonija go elfahle ni á jo fahl Solomon, mehle tahm song tub ejahm go atang nya jolo go egudu njom.  
\v 51 Bo kehm tongo Solomon re, <<Adonija kpꞌfahle ntula Solomon, yebsong tub ejahm go atang nya egudu njom. Á bungu re, <<Nong ntula Solomon tir tong-m lela re, á nehm wul me nlokeltum ewe.>>> 
\p  
\v 52 Solomon kehm faange re, <<Á lꞌtib elne ana nne no bo bahk-e ma bum etingitingi, jol ellv esi ene anehng anehng nehm gbo go ndi; wo lꞌjol re abꞌbi bahke jolo go ege atahng, á bahke kpoko.>>  
\v 53 Owo Ntula Solomon kehm tumu ane, bo song radd-e go egudu njom ba a ne. Owo Adonija kehm bake, ba gbo kohk esi go ndi kpunu Ntula Solomon, owo Solomon kehm bungu tong-e re, <<Song ega etahk.>> 
\c 2  
\s1 Esꞌkohro Elle Ni Devid tubu Solomon 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ngare ba rehng nyi Devid yahke ba elkpoko, á tubu Solomon mmon ewe elle. 
\p  
\v 2 Á kehm bungu re, <<N yahke ba eltahme mbang nyi anebe njini kpee bahke jeke. Yiimi tꞌtahne, tib elna re wo nnenlum wo,  
\v 3 wo fere jo toono ji Jehova Esowo eba kpꞌsebe re wo toono. Jo jen go ege abang, wo jo bum ntibi a nkahn enye, atahm a nsol nyi á kpꞌsebe re wo lim, ana nya bo nyono go atahm nya Mosis, eji lꞌnob a na go ejum ajehng ajehng ji á kpꞌlimi, a edi ajehng ajehng ji a kpꞌjeke,  
\v 4 eji Jehova lꞌbum enyam abehng abehng bi a nyame tong-m: <Lꞌjol re etˈtohngo eja bahke kunu elbo ekpu ana bo kpꞌbumu nkpin ebo, fere jol go etingitingi go egame esamahr a ntim a ntim ebo, a ntira ntir ebo, a nehm tiki rin elbele nne no bahke kuumu etul bi Isreel.> 
\p  
\v 5 Anv, wofono antahng kpꞌkahne ji Joab mmona Jeruya lim-m no- ji á limi atubesi nsoja na abal ba Isreel, Abner mmona Ner, a Amasa mmona Jeda. Á wulu bo, wohng alung ngare elkoono, ano are ngare ebta nyi, alung me-e taame go egbaange ji li-e go ebun tete rehng go akpaketa enye go akpade.  
\v 6 Jabb-e nobnob ana elkahne ena li no, fvfo ka taame á kul, yel go ndi elahm soom.  
\v 7 "Lub tib abone Bajilayi ji Giled nnoobo eljini, nong bo woomo go ellong ane ba bahke jo li go ega ekpukuru. Bo tob-m sehng ngare nyi n jo be Absalom mmonane. 
\p  
\v 8 <<Fvfo buumu re, Semeyi mmona Gera li a na, nnea Benjamin no lohng go ejahbe ji bo kpo lung re Bahurim, ye ji biri akuk tv-m efung bi n je go Mahanayim. Ngare nyi á ba ba kpir-m go aya ma Jodan, n tiri tong-e go mbing nyi Jehova re: <N wa nehm tiki wul go ekahngkahng.>  
\v 9 Wo anv, ke-e ko ana nne no ki lim ebi. Wo nne no kpi elkahne wo; a bahke kahne ji a bahk-e limi. Toobo ana a bahk-e wulu, ka taame á kul.>> 
\p  
\v 10 Owo Devid kehm kpoko bo song kpa-e kak go ejahbe ji Devid.  
\v 11 Á fili Isreel nnya atahl abal, nnya esehma á jolo go Hebron jo fili edi, eltahl a nnya ewubu a nya era á jolo go Jeusalem jo fili edi.  
\v 12 Ano wo Solomon ji go eti etul ji nde Devi, wo eti etul eje kehm tahne fere gbˈgbal. 
\s1 Eti etul Ji Solomon yiimi tˈtahne 
\p  
\v 13 Ano wo Adonija, mmona Hagiti kehm tahme goji Betiseba nnyehna Solomon. Betiseba kehm-e bahbe re, <<Á baa a ntir elkoono go ega atahnga?> 
\p Á kehm faange re, <<Ee, go elkoono.>>  
\v 14 Owo á kehm kpe bung budu re, <<N kpi ejum ji n kpꞌsebe re me m bung a na.>> 
\p Á kehm-e faange re, <<A bahke ma bung.>>  
\v 15 Á kehm bungu re, <<A kpꞌkahne re, Eti etul jia jolo jꞌjame. Isreel kpee jo seenge me ana ntul a bo. Wo nsol yaange, eti etul feere goji mmonannee; wo je go ege, tib lohng goji Jehova. 
\p  
\v 16 Anv, ejum ajehng ji n kpꞌbahbe go ega. Kama ten.>> Á kehm-e tongo re, <<Á bahke ma bahb.>> 
\p  
\v 17 Ano wo á soro asi re, <<Titi bahb ntula Solomon, re á ka-m Abisag nnea Sunem á jol nkal ewame. Wo ega n kpˈkahne re á nehm ten ejum ajehng ajehng ji a bahb-e no.  
\v 18 Betiseba kehm faange re <<Ebnob sehng. M bahke bungu a ntul ka-a.>> 
\p  
\v 19 Eji Betiseba je goji ntula Solomon re á song bung ka Adonija, ntul mehle song wane Betiseba, song gong kak-e, feere song ji go go ege eti etul. Á tongo bo ko eti etul ba ka nnyehn ntul. Betiseba jii go eti go ege ejang eboblum. 
\p  
\v 20 Nnyehn kehm bungu re, <<N kpꞌsebe re me m bahb-a mmojum ntiil, titi kama ten.>> 
\p Ntul kehm faange re, <<Bahb, nnee; ji a lꞌbahb n nehm ten.>> 
\p  
\v 21 Owo á kehm bungu re, <<Nong bo rod Abisag nnea Sunem ka mmonanne Adonija go elbal.>> 
\p  
\v 22 Ntula Solomon kehm faange nnyehn re, <<Jenji wahnge a kpꞌbahbe re me n rod Abisag nnea Sunem ka Adonija? A jol tob, bahb eti etul ka-e, tibre ye mmonannee no nkul wo. Ee, bahb eti etul ka-e, tob ka Abiata ji nlimajom, a Joab ji mmona Jeruya!>>  
\v 23 Owo ntula Solomon kehm tiri go mbing nyi Jehova re, <<Esowo lim bib aname sab bˈbib, tohko jol re Adonija bahke kake elkpin ene eji á bahbe ejum jia!  
\v 24 Anv, etingitingi eji Jehova li go elkpin, ye ji ma-m lim re me n gbal fere tahne go eti etul ji nso Devid, yeb lennge nji etul nyia ka-m ana á nyame no, lela Adonija bo bahk-e wulu!>>  
\v 25 Ano wo Solomon ka Benaya mmona Jehoiada nsahm, á song wul Adonija. 
\p  
\v 26 Ntul bungu tong Abiata nlimajom re, <<Feere song kehnge go ega etahk go Anatoti. Wo fꞌfuumu re wo kpo, wo anv sang m bahk-a wulu, tib a solo Elkohl Atahm ni nsoo ntula Jehova ji Gbale Sehng, go esamahr nso ewame Devid, fere toono nyehn erem a nso go ajahkjahk.>>  
\v 27 Ano wo Solomon yehke Abiata go eltum abalimajom ni Jehova. Go mbang ana nyia alum nya Jehova bungu no go Silo bade etahk ji Elayi bˈbiingi go nseenga seenge.  
\v 28 Eji etib rehnge Joab, ye ji woomo ntoobo nyio a Adonija, jol á woomem ellong ni Absalom, á kehm beke song yel ebkpatahk bi Jehova, song tub ejahm go atang nya li go egudu njom.  
\v 29 Bo kehm tongo ntula Solomon re, Joab ebbe song yel go ebkpatahk bi Jehova, fere song yiimi go nkpe egudu njom. Owo Solomon kehm fake Benaya mmona Jehoiada nnyo re, <<Song wo song wul-e!>> 
\p  
\v 30 Ano wo Benaya yele go ebkpatahk ni Jehova, kehm tongo Joab re, <Ntul re, wo lohng elatahk. >> 
\p Wo á faange re, <<Eꞌee, m bahke kpoko a.>> 
\p Benaya feere song tong ntul re, <Ana wo Joab faang-m no.>  
\v 31 Owo ntul kehm kake Benaya elkahn re, <<Lim ana á bungu no. Wul-e tub, wo kpa-e kak, eji me a nnahb enyame kpee lꞌkˈli ebi ji alung mbol mbol ma Joab wohngo no.  
\v 32 Jehova bahk-e kpiki go esi ji alung ma á ma wul ane wohng, tib jol nso ewame Devid kahnem, á mehle song nok ane abal, wul bo go ekahngkahng. Bo ane abal abal, Abner mmona Ner, ye ji jolo ntubesia nsoja no Isreel, a Amasa mmona Jeter, ntubesia nsoja no Juda, bo jolo atingitingi ane ba nobo sehnge ye.  
\v 33 Nong ebi ji alung ebo kuumu go esi ji Joab, a etˈtohngo eje go njinanjini. Wo goji Devid, a etˈtohngo eje, etahk eje a eti etul eje, nong elkoono ni Jehova jol o go njinanjini.>> 
\p  
\v 34 Ano wo Benaya mmona Jehoiada mehle no song yel go ebkpatahk song wul Joab, bo fere song kpa-e kak go ege edi ndi go elka emahng.  
\v 35 Ntul kehm limi Benaya mmona Jehoiada ntubesia nsoja go nji nyi Joab, fvfo nji nyi Abiata ntul rodo ka Jadok ji nlimajom. 
\p  
\v 36 Owo ntul kehm tumu re bo ko Semeyi ba, á kehm-e tongo re, <<Si etahk eja a Jeusalem, wo lene o, fvfo ka kpe tiki lohng tahm edi ajehng ajehng.  
\v 37 Efung bi á lꞌlohng siiri edamme ji Kidron, tiki kahn re a bahke kpoko, alung ema bahke kuumu wofono antahng.>> 
\p  
\v 38 Simeyi kehm faange ntul re, <<Ji a ma bung kpꞌnobo. Me nlokeltum ewa bahke limi ji wo nsoo ewame ma bung.>> Simeyi sa go Jeusalem ekidi lꞌlab. 
\p  
\v 39 Eji ma kang nnya era, nju na ebal nyi Simeyi kehm beke tahm goji Akisi mmona Maaka, ntula Gati, fvfo etib kehm ba kpiri Simeyi re, <<Aju enya li go Gati.>>  
\v 40 Eji Simeyi wuku ano, á kehm kuumu go ege mbvankang tahm goji Akisi go Gati, re á song seb aju enye. Ano wo Simeyi mehle no tahm go Gati song ko aju enye feere abo. 
\p  
\v 41 Eji bo tongo Solomon re Simeyi eblohng a Jerusalem je go Gati feere,  
\v 42 ntul kehm lungu Simeyi tv elne, fere tong-e re, <<Me wa n limem á tir go mbing nyi Jehova, n fere ka-a erehke re, <<Go efung bi a lꞌyake edi jia tahm edi jindikandiki, wo bahke kahne re a bahke tiki kpoa? Go ngare nyio a tong-m re, <<Ji a bungu no ebnob. M bahke wuku.>>  
\v 43 Nꞌnan á ki bum nwongo nyi a ko no a Jehova, fere bum elkahn ni n ka-a no?> 
\p  
\v 44 Ntul tob bungu tong Simeyi re, <<A kpꞌkahne go ega eltim, abꞌbi nya a limi nsoo ewame Devid. Anv, Jehova bahk-a kpiki go abꞌbi enya nya a limi no.  
\v 45 Fvfo ntula Solomon bahke bele na elfuulu, Eti etul ji Devid bahke sake yiimi ano tˈtahne go esamahr bi Jehova go njinanjini.>> 
\p  
\v 46 Owo ntul kehm kake Benaya mmona Jehoiada nsahm, á song Simeyi. 
\p Etul kehm gbale tahne go abo nya Solomon. 
\c 3  
\s1 Solomon Bahbe Esowo Ngbere 
\p  
\v 1 Solomon kehm limi etem a Fero ntula Ijib, fere ko mmona ewe go elbal. Á ko nkal noo ba go ejahbe ji Devid, tete á si ekpasiki eje, a etahk ji Jehova, go ekahme ji sennge Jeusalem kak mal.  
\v 2 Ana jolo o ngare nyia anebe Isreel kpi nlimi nlim ajom go agudu njom nya bo limi antahng, tibre go ngare nyia bo ka si etahk Esowo ji bo bahke jo kpunu Mbing nyi Jehova.  
\v 3 Solomon tibi elkoro ene ni á kpi a Jehova, eji á jo bum ntibi nyi Devid nde ka-e no, sehngem re á jo limi ajom fere jo fi insen agudu ajom nya bo limi antahng. 
\p  
\v 4 Efung abehng ntul mehle tahm go Gibion song lim ajom, tib go wo agudu njom nya ga fuumu jolo no, fvfo Solomon limi ajom nkpel atahl alon alon go edi ebwubu, nya eljahme fi go egudu njom jio.  
\v 5 Go Gibion wo Jehova ba kpir-e go nlem nlum atv, Esowo tong-e re, <<Bahb ejum ajehng ajehng ji á kpꞌsebe re me n ka-a.>> 
\p  
\v 6 Solomon kehm faange re, <<Wobtib nlokeltum ewa, Devid nsoo ewame, nnoobo eljini ena, tibre á bele ekakesehk jol etingi nne, fvfo eltim ene jolo tortor. Wob soro asi go egburu nnoobo eljini ana nia ka-e, fere ka-e mmon no ma ji go ege eti etul efung bi lela. 
\p  
\v 7 <<Anv, Jehova Esowo ebame, wobbob me nlokeltum ewa etul go nji nyi nsoo Devid. Wo ga, me mmonse wo, fvfo n nehme kahn ana m bahke ma jo lim ntum enyame.  
\v 8 Me nlokeltum ewa noa a, go ellong ane ba a ma yehke, agburu ane, bobrur sehng re, nne nehm ma nfange.  
\v 9 Fvfo lub ka nlokeltum ewa ngbere nyi eltim, nyi m bahke jo fili ane eba, ana m bahke jo kahn ejum ji nno a ji kpꞌsabe.Tibre nne awoo bahke ma kahn ana á bahke ma fili egburu ellong ane eba baa?>> 
\p  
\v 10 Jehova atahng yebe sehng eji Solomon bahbe ejum jia.  
\v 11 Owo Esowo kehm-e tongo re, <<Eji á ma bahb ejum jia, a bahbem bade nlabe elkpin, afi afang ka elna, jol elkv wul anebekv eba sang á bahbe no, á bahbe bade ngbere nyi eltim, nyi a bahke jo lam elam ji nno,  
\v 12 M bahke limi ji a bahbe no. M bahk-a kake elkahne a ngbere nyi eltim, eji bahke jolo re nnene ka tohko jol ana wo, fvfo nnene nehm tiki jol ana wo go afung esˈsong.  
\v 13 Budu o m bahk-a kake ji a ki bahb. M bahk-a afang, a ekpunu, eji ngare nyi a kpeka li go elkpin ntul limm no bo bahk-e koko gaare a na.  
\v 14 A lꞌjen go egame abang, fere jo bum ntibi enyame a nkahn ana nso Devid jo bum, m bahk-a kake nlabe elkpin.>>  
\v 15 Owo Solomon kehm nyahme, á sebe kahn re nlem nyi. 
\p Á kehm feere go Jeusalem, kehm song yiimi go esamahr elkohl atahm ni Jehova, lim ajom nya eljahme fi, a ajom nya elkoono. Á kehm limi elkak ka anebe eltum ebe kpee. 
\s1 Solomon Kimi Elam Ji Nno 
\p  
\v 16 Efung abehng anebkal asꞌsa na abal kehm bake goji ntul, ba yiimi go ege esamahr.  
\v 17 Awohng kehm bungu re, <<Nsoo ntul ewame, nyehnem ndon, nnenkal noa a me, e lene etahk ajehng. N jele mmon eji á jolo o aname.  
\v 18 Eji ma kang nfung era nyi n jele no, nnenkal noa tob jel mmon. E jolo wahr wahr etahk; nnene jolem o anahre, wahr ane abal ba jolo. 
\p  
\v 19 <<Ngare atv, nnenkal noa mmon ewe ba kpo, tib á noongo nyed-e tv.  
\v 20 Á kehm mehle nlum atv, fere rod mmon ewame go egame elwo, eji me nlokeltum ewa kpꞌlale. Á kehm song bum-e go ege nnyo elbel, fere rod no we no ma kpo ba bum-m go egame nnyo elbel.  
\v 21 Etoono efungfu, n kehm mehle re me n ka mmon ewame, abel n sebe kahn re yeb kpo! Eji n seeng-e no nobnob eji edi ma lennge, n sebe kahn re a mmon no n jele no sang.>> 
\p  
\v 22 Nnenkal noko re, <<Eꞌee! No li elkpin wo li no ewame; no ma kpo wo li no wa.>> 
\p Wo ngbokambang nnenkal tiki yiimi re, <<Eꞌee! mmon no ma kpo wo li no wa, no li go elkpin wo li no ewame.>> Ano wo bo jo faabe go esamahr ntul. 
\p  
\v 23 Ntul kehm bungu re, <<Noa kpꞌbungu re, <Mmon ewame wo li go elkpin, wo no ewa ebkpo,> Wo noko re, <Eꞌee, Mmon ewa ebkpo, no ewame wo li elkpin.> >> 
\p  
\v 24 Owo ntul kehm bungu re, <<Koon ekahngkahng ba ka-m.>>Owo bo kehm koko ekahngkahng ba ka ntul.  
\v 25 Á kehm kake bo elkahn re<<Kimen mmon noa no li go elkpin ekpidi na ebbal, wahn ka noka ekpidi lehko, fere ka noko ekpidi jehko.>> 
\p  
\v 26 Wo nnenkal no mmon ewe jolo elkpin, elkoro gbal-e atahng sehng bade esi mmon ewe, á kehm bungu tong ntul re, <<Titi nsoo ewame, ka-e mmon no li go elkpin! Ke-e wul!>> 
\p Wo nnenkal noko re, <<Jolo me afi wo, nnene nehm ko mmon noa. Kimen ye ekpidi ebbal!>>  
\v 27 Owo ntul kehm kimi elam eje re: Kaan ngbokambang nnenkal noo mmon no li go elkpin. Kana ye wul, ye wo li nnyehn.>> 
\p  
\v 28 Eji anebe Isreel kpee wuku elam ji ntul ma kimi, bo mehle ekpunu ji bo kpi a ntul sahb wˈwahre, tibre bo nyehne re elkahne ene lohng goji Esowo bade ekimi elam ji nno. 
\c 4  
\s1 Abalimeltum Solomon A Ane Ba Jo Fili Adi 
\p  
\v 1 Ano wo Ntula Solomon fili Isreel kpee.  
\v 2 A wo li agburu ane ba jo lim eltum a ne: Ajariya mmona Jadok wo jolo nlimajom;  
\v 3 Elihoref abola Ahija, abon ba Sisa, bo ba jolo abanyonawer; Jehosafati mmona Elilud ye wo jo nyon nsol bum;  
\v 4 Benaya mmona Jehoiada- jolo ntubesia nsoja; Jadok abola Abiata- bo ba jolo abalimajom;  
\v 5 Ajaria mmona Natan- ye wo jolo nne no atubesi ba jo fili arohko ajahbe woom-e go elwo; Jabud mmona Natan jolo nlimajom a nne no jo tub ntul elle;  
\v 6 Ahisa- jo kpuru ekpasiki; Adoniram mmona Abda ye wo jolo ntubesi ane ba jo bob ane bo lim ntum. 
\p  
\v 7 Solomon bele atubesi eltum ewubu ane abal ba jo fili arohko adi go Isreel kpee, bo ji jo ko nsol alehke a nsol nyehko goji anebe Isreel ba ka ntul a anebe etahk ebe. No nne jo ko nsol go ege erohko edi nnyahng amehng go elya ba ka etahk ntul.  
\v 8 Abing ebo nya a: Ben-Hur jolo ka erohko ejahbe ewong ji Efriim;  
\v 9 Ben-Deker jol ka arohko ajahbe nya Makaji, Salbim, Beti Semesi a Elon Beti-Hanan;  
\v 10 Ben-Hesed jol ka Aruboti (Soko a ndi nyi Hefer kpee jolo nyˈnye);  
\v 11 Ben- Abinadab jol ka Nafoti Dor ( á koo Tafati mmona Solomon go elbal);  
\v 12 Baana mmona Ahilud jol ka Taanak, Megido, a Beti San kpee ji li toono Jaretan erede bi Jejireel, bomo go Beti San rehng Abel Mehola siiri rehng Jokmiam;  
\v 13 Ben-Geber-jolo ka Ramoti Giled, a abona ajahbe ba li Giled nya jolo ka ebangenahb ji Jair mmona Manase. Á tob jolo ntubesi go erohko ji agob go Basan, ji Bele ejahbe atahl ara nya bo lange akahme sennge kak, ko abilikpi lim nti elbame go ebo ati mbu.  
\v 14 Ahinadab mmona Edo jol ka Mahanaim;  
\v 15 Ahimaji jolo ka Naftali (á koo Basemati mmona Solomon go elbal);  
\v 16 Baana mmona Husayi jolo ka Aser a Aloti;  
\v 17 Jehosafati mmona Parua jolo ka Isaka;  
\v 18 Simeyi mmona Ela jol ka Benjamin;  
\v 19 Geber mmona Uri jolo ka Giled eji jolo ejahbe ji Sihon ntul no anebe Amor a ejahbe ji Og ntula Basan. Geber ntahng ntahng wo jolo ntubesi no fili erohko jio. 
\s1 Nsol Afang Nya Solomon 
\p  
\v 20 Anebe Juda a anebe Isreel bo ruru are eriki bi li go nkpe agburu aya bi; bo li nsol, fere wꞌwo, bel eyebatahng.  
\v 21 Owo Solomon jo fili ajahbe kpee, bomo go aya ma Ufrati song rehng go ndi nyi anebe Filista, tete song rehng go nkonandi nyi Ijib. Ajahbe nyaa kpee jo tahbe ntahbe ka Solomon, fere woom-e go elwo ngare nyi á jolo go elkpin kpee.  
\v 22 Nsol nyi bo jo ko le Solomon a anebe etahk ebe go efung abehng, jo jolo ebusel abe atahl asehma ebusel ebwubu, a ebusel akahde kahde abe atahlku,  
\v 23 efong ewubu bi joko jok, edahmagbudu eltahl bi bo ma le bo, a ejoro go ebul atahl alon, fvfo abilikpa a nrahng, go ngu nyi kpi atang nya kpi ayal, a ekok bi nno a nno.  
\v 24 Tib á jo fili ajahbe nya jolo erede aya ma Ufrati, bomo go Tifsa rehng go Gaja, fvfo elkoono jolo ajang kpe kpe.  
\v 25 Ngare nyi Solomon jolo elkpin Juda a Isreel, bomo go Dan rehng go Beeseba, ntong anyehng anyehng jolem, ebangenahb ajehng ajehng bele ebgbe agreb nya bo, afik nya bo jo ko le elbo.  
\v 26 Adi nya Solomon jo kuuru amvtv anyꞌnya jolo edi atahl alon alon nkpel atahltahl. Anyꞌnya jolo enyꞌnya atahl alon alon nkpel atahlarakara.  
\v 27 Atubesi arohko adi jo bele ekakesehk jo ka Ntula Solomon nsol alehke a ane ba jo ba go ekpuru ntul. Ntubesi awohng awohng jo tiki seb kahn re ejumjum jolem go elehng go nnyahng mi jolo mˈme.  
\v 28 Nfiladi awohng awohng jo ko nkohl abali a ajele ana bo tong-e no ba bum edi ji fuumu no, eji lˈjol ka anyˈnya nya kpo fing amvtv akuungu a anyˈnya nyako. 
\s1 Ngbere Nyi Solomon 
\p  
\v 29 Esowo ka Solomon ngbere, a ntir atahng nyi sahb gbˈgbal, a ekahnafem ji nne lˈkˈma ko gare.  
\v 30 Ngbere nyi Solomon gbale sehnge ngbere nyi ane kpee ba lohng go ero nfam, tob gbal sehnge ngbere kpee nyi anebe Ijib.  
\v 31 Á bele ngbere sehnge anebe ngbere bako kpee, sehnge Etan nnea Ejira, á bele ngbere sehnge Heman, Kalkol a Darda abon ba Mahol. Elgahm ene yeere tete rehng go ajahbe kpee nya li sennge bo kak.  
\v 32 Á tuubu ngaane atahl alon alon go eltahl a nkpel ewubu, ase enye jolo ese atahl alon alon nkpel ewubu a ese eblon.  
\v 33 Á jo bungu bade elkpin ni nti, bomo go eseda ji Bebilon rehng go hisob ji kpo mahng go akahme. Á tob bungu bada enyam kpee bi kpo tohng ala go ndi.  
\v 34 Atul kpee ba njini ba wuku bada ngbere nyi Solomon, jo tumu ane go ajahbe kpee re bo ba wuk ngbere nyi Solomon. 
\c 5  
\s1 Ntoobo Nyi Elsehke Etahk Esowo 
\p  
\v 1 Eji Hiram ntula Taya wuku re Solomon bo me-e bob etul re á ko nji nyi nde Devid, á kehm tumu ntiingi etib ewe tv Solomon, tibre á jolo etem ngare kpe kpe a Devid.  
\v 2 Solomon feere tum etib bia tv Hiram re:  
\v 3 <<A kpꞌkahne re tib go nta nyi bo noko a nsoo Devid go ejang abehng abehng, á maam si etahk Esowo ji bo bahke jo kak mbing nyi Jehova Esowo ebe. Jehova bahk-e limi re, a jo ga anebekv ebe.  
\v 4 Wo anv Jehova Esowo ebame ma-m ka erekekv go ejang abehng abehng, anebekv afi enok limm.  
\v 5 N kpi ntir fvfo nyi m bahke sehke Etahk Esowo ji bo bahke jo kak mbing nyi Jehova Esowo ebame, ana Jehova tongo nsoo Devid, eji á bungu re, <Mmon ewa, ye ji m bahk-e kunu go eti etul toon-a, ye wo bahke sehke Etahk Esowo ka mbing enyame.>  
\v 6 <<Anv fvfo ka elkahn bo gbakke aseda nya Lebanon ba ka-m. Ane ebame bahke limi eltum a ane eba, m bahke kpiki ane eba ekun bi á lꞌtaame. A kpꞌkahne re wahr kpimm ane ba kpi elwak ni agburu nti agbakke ana anebe Sodon.>>  
\v 7 Eji Hiram wuku etib bi Solomon, atahng yebe sꞌsehng, á fere bung re, <<Eltehke jol ka Jehova lela, tib yeb ka Devid Mmon ewe no kpi ngbere re á fili egburu ejahbe jia.>> 
\p  
\v 8 Owo Hiram kehm tumu ellum tv Solomon re: Me n wuk etib bi a tumu tv-m, m bahke limi ajehng ajehng bade aseda a akv nti junipa nya a kpˈsebe.  
\v 9 Alokeltum ebame bahke bannge bomo go Lebanon tete ba rehng go agburu aya ma Mediteran, bo bahke tuuru kak jo fab go aya tete ba rehng edi ji a bahke tibi. Owo bo bahke fannge, eji a bahke ma rod tahm a nya. M bahke sebe re wo lim ji m bahbe no bade nsol alehke nyi a bahke kake ane kpee ba lohng ga egame etahk ntul.>> 
\p  
\v 10 Go mbang nyia Hiram soro asi jo ka Solomon aseda kpee a akv nti junipa nya á kpꞌsebe,  
\v 11 fvfo Solomon kaa Hiram ebusel nkohl atahltahl nkpel atahl awubbal ebusel ebwubu, ana nsol alehke ka nlaaga Hiram, fere budu egalon akehng oliv ma bo ma kaame, atahltahl nkpel atahl awubu era a egalon elku. Solomon soro asi jo lim jia ka Hiram go elya elya.  
\v 12 Jehova ka Solomon ngbere, jang jang ana á nyame no tong-e. Hiram abola Solomon jolo go elkoono, bo ko nwongo nyi elkoono atemtem.  
\v 13 Ntula Solomon yehke ane atahltahl nkpel atahl ara a nkpel elku, go ellong anebe Isreel kpee, ba a bahke jo bob bo, bo lim atahntahn ntum enye.  
\v 14 Á jo tumu bo tv go Lebanon go ellong ellong, ellong anehng anehng jo jolo ane atahltahl go eltahl a nkpele elon, bo jo kange nnyahng amehng go Lebanon, fere feere ba kang nnyahng ebal go etahk. Adoniram wo jolo ntubesi, eltum ni bo jo bob ane jo lim.  
\v 15 Solomon bele ane atahltahl nkpel atahlawubu ba jo soongo atal, ane ba jo sol atal jolo ane atahltahl nkpel atahl asehma a nkpel elku,  
\v 16 á tob bele atubesi ane atahltahl nkpel atahl ani a nkpel ebal ane atahl awubu, ba jo fili ane bao kpee go eltum, jo tib bo ana bo bahke jo lim.  
\v 17 Go elkahn ni ntul, bo yehke agburu atal nya nno nya bo soongo no, nya bo yahke ko bom nnahb ekahme nyi etahk Esowo.  
\v 18 Aneb eltum ba Solomon a ba Hiram, go aneblum ba Gebal kiimi akv nti, fere fik atal bum abasehke ntahk ba etahk Esowo. 
\c 6  
\s1 Solomon Si Etahk Esowo 
\p  
\v 1 Go nnya atahltahl a nnya atahlani nyi anebe Isreel lohngo eju go Ijib, ngare nyia Solomon ebfili Isreel nnya eni, go nnyahng mi bo kpo lung re Jiv, mi jolo etoono nnyahng go elya, owo Solomon bomo etahk Jehova go elsehke  
\v 2 Etahk ji Ntula Solomon sii ka Jehova, alab jolo ntahme atahl abal a ntahme elon, akpang jolo ntahme elku, elkul ero jolo eltahl a ntahme ebal kunu esi.  
\v 3 Bo ramme ago kak gbiiri elbultahk ni bo junu no, elbultahk nio go mbuksong Etahk Esowo kpange rehng ntahme elku, akpange jolo jangjang ana mbuksong etahk Esowo. Labe lohng rehng ntahme esehma kunu esi go mbuksong etahk Esowo.  
\v 4 Á limi abon abu nkpe akahme fiidi ga elatahk go atahng kpˈkpange.  
\v 5 Á si eyong nkpake era lake go ekahme ji jolo sennge egburu ekpˈkpa, ji nkimi nyi li saang. Go mbang nyio á kake anyo ekpˈkpa gbalee sennge etahk jio.  
\v 6 Akpang ekpˈkpa ji nnahba ndi sa ntiil rehng ntahme eni, akpang nya ekpˈkpa ji li nkpake anyehng jolo ntahme eni kunu esi, akpang ekpˈkpa nkpake era jolo ntahme ewubu kunu esi. Á lange nsol sennge etahk Esowo go elatahk, eji bo lꞌkꞌrahm ejum ajehng ajehng kak akahme etahk Esowo.  
\v 7 Eji bo jo lang etahk Esowo, atal nya bo soongo no go edi atal awake nya nya bo ko jo lang, fvfo ngan anyehng anyehng, ejum ji bo kpo ko fik, afi ekuungu ajehng ajehng jehko ji eltum alimi nne kpeem wuk ewahl eje go edi ji bo jo si etahk Esowo.  
\v 8 Edi elyele go Etahk Esowo go nkpake nyi ndi, jolo ejang eboblum nfam bi etahk Esowo; edi elwahre jolo o rehng go ngbokambanga nkpake, fere tob sehng o rehng nkpake nyi ero.  
\v 9 Ano wo á lange etahk Esowo, fere lim mal, kum agburu ajang nti, a ajang nti aseda go elbulu.  
\v 10 Á si abon ntahk lake go akpꞌkpe etahk Esowo kpee. Elkul ero nya abon nkpatahk bao sa ntiil rehng ntahme eni, bo ko ajang nti eseda nya nnen kum lake etahk Esowo. 
\p  
\v 11 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Solomon re:  
\v 12 <<Bade etahk Esowo jia ji a kpꞌsehke, lꞌjol re a bahke toono ntibi enyame, lim nsol nyi m ma-a tib, fere bum nkahn enyame kpee, kpunu atahm nyaa, m bahke limi sehng go ega biingi go nseenga nseenge ana n nyame tong nso Devid.  
\v 13 M bahke lene go ellong ni anebe Isreel, fvfo n nehm yake Isreel ane ebame.>> 
\p  
\v 14 Ano wo Solomon si etahk Esowo, fere lim mal.  
\v 15 Á koo akpakenti aseda kum lake go akahme nya atahng ekpˈkpa, bomo go ndi tete rehng go ero etahk, tob ko akpakenti nya Junipa bulu go elka ndi.  
\v 16 Á koo akpakenti lim nkimi, akpang jolo ntahme elku, go nkpe ekpꞌkpa etahk Esowo, bo kumu akpakenti bomo ndi tete rehng go ero etahk, lim mmonkimi, no sahb lˈli saang.  
\v 17 Nkpange kpange ekpꞌkpa ji li mbuksong ekpꞌkpa jia, jolo eltahl a ntahme ewubu go alab.  
\v 18 Go atahng etahk Esowo bo ko ajangenti aseda, fik ntuku a atꞌtuul nya ma nyange. Ejum ajehng ajehng bo ko ajangenti aseda lim; eltal ekahme anehng anehng bo sebem re bo nyehn.  
\v 19 Bo toobo edi go atahng nkimi ji li saang ji li go nkpe etahk nyi njahmtahk Etahk Esowo, elkohl nwongo nyi Jehova o.  
\v 20 Nkimi nyi atahng nyi jolo saang, jolo ntahme elku, alab, akpang a elkul ero. Á koo nnyam nyam agul taame kpee go ekpꞌkpa, á tob taame agul egudu njom jio ji aseda.  
\v 21 Solomon ko nnyam nyama agul wohng bulu kpee go atahng ekpꞌkpa etahk Esowo, fvfo á tanne ngbekobo agul, nyi siiri mbutahk mi atahng nkimi nyi li saang, go mbuksonga nkimi nyi li saang nyi bo wohngo agul bulu.  
\v 22 Ano wo á wohngo agul go akpꞌkpa kpee. Á tob wohngo agul go egudu njom ji jolo ka nkimi nyi atahng ekpꞌkpa ji li saang. 
\p  
\v 23 Go ekpꞌkpa ji atahng ji li saang, á ko eti oliv lim eserabim ebbal, ajehng ajehng wahre elkul ero rehng ntahme esehma kunu esi.  
\v 24 Ekpungkpung ji ngbokambang eserabim labe rehng ntahme ebal kunu esi, ekpungkpung jehko tob jolo ntahme ebal kunu esi, kpe kpe bomo esi ekpungkpung jehko rehng esi ekpungkpung jehka jolo ntahme esehma kunu esi go alab.  
\v 25 Go etoono eserubim, bo tob gare alab ekpungkpung jolo ntahme esehma kunu esi, eserub ebbal ebbal jolo elkohn anehng alab a eljini ni bo li no.  
\v 26 Elkul ero ji eserub ajehng ajehng jolo ntahme esehma kunu esi.  
\v 27 Á rodo aserub nyao bum go atahng nkimi nyi li saang etahk Esowo. Ekpungkpung ji eserub ajehng kooro ekahme jehko , ekpungkpung ji eserub jehka kooro ekahme jehka, fvfo go elka elka ekpꞌkpa akpungkpung ebo ba kooro atemtem.  
\v 28 Á koo agul wohng bulu aserub nyao kpee. 
\p  
\v 29 Go akahme kpee nya atahng ekpꞌkpa a nya elatahk, á fiki aserubim, arahn mbohng, a atꞌtuul nya ma nyange.  
\v 30 Á tob wohngo agul bulu go elka ndi akpꞌkpa nya li elꞌlohng elꞌlohng, a akpꞌkpa nya li go atahng. 
\p  
\v 31 Bo mbutahk mi atahng ekpꞌkpa ji li saang, á ko nti oliv lim abutahk nya edi ji li saang, nya kpange rehng ntahme era.  
\v 32 Go mbutahk ebal mi bo ko eti oliv lim, á fiki eserabim, arahn mbohng, a atꞌtuul nya ma nyange, fere ko agul nya bo dv no wohng bulu eserabim a arahn mbohng nyao.  
\v 33 Go mbang nyꞌnehm nyi á limi nti mbutahk nyi kpi ngoongo eni eni, mi bo ko nti oliv lim mbutahk mi li rehng egburu ekpꞌkpa.  
\v 34 Á ko eti ji bo kpo lung re sipres tob lim mbutahk ebal mi jo fehd na, amehng amehng bo limi re jo fehd ntahng ntahng.  
\v 35 Á fiki aserabim, arahn mbohng, a atꞌtuul nya ma nyange lake go abutahk, fere wohng agul nya bo ma kahd bulu nsol nyi bo ma fik. 
\p  
\v 36 Á lange atahng nlaaga go atal nya bo soongo no, go ero nkpa era anyehng anyehng bo jo kunu egburu ejang nti eseda. 
\p  
\v 37 Nnahb ekahme nyi etahk Esowo bo bumu go nnya eni nyi Solomon kuumu etul, go nnyahng mi bo kpo lung re Jiv ji jolo nnyahng era go elya.  
\v 38 Go ewubu elya anehng, go nnyahng mi bo kpo lung re Bul, mi jolo nnyahng enehkeni, bo si etahk Esowo mal, a nsol kpee nyi bo kake ana bo tibi bo. Á ko nnya esehma go elsehke. 
\c 7  
\s1 Solomon Si Ekpasiki Eje 
\p  
\v 1 Solomon ko ewuba nnya era kohro kohro si ekpasiki eje mal.  
\v 2 Ekp'kpa ajehng go akp'kpa nya ekpasiki eje bo jo lungu re Etahk Ntul ji Ekulugbe Lebanon, alab jolo ntahme atahl ani a ntahme enehkeni, akpang jolo ntahme atahlabal a ntahme eni ewubu kunu esi, elkul ero jolo eltahl a ntahme esehma. Nti ago aseda na eni, nya jo gbiiri ajangenti asi ekahme aseda nya bo ma soongo.  
\v 3 Aseda nya bo ko kum bulu ajangenti asi akahme, jolo ejangenti asi akahme atahl abal ejangenti eblon, ego elku elku go nti anyehng anyehng.  
\v 4 Abonbu nkpe ekahme ekpꞌkpa jolo nkpake era, jolo wane atemtem.  
\v 5 Abutahk kpee a atimbutahk jo bele nkpohko eni eni, jolo nkpake era wane atemtem. 
\p  
\v 6 Á tob lange ekpꞌkpa ji ago, bulu molbulu, alab jolo ntahme atahlabal a ntahme eni, akpang jolo eltahl a ntahme esehma. Edi eljehke jolo labe labe go mbuksong bo kake ago jabbe.  
\v 7 Solomon tob si ekp'kpa eti etul, ji jolo ekpꞌkpa elam alame, ji á bahke jo ji jo lam alam, ko aseda bulu bomo ndi tete rehng go ero atahng ekpꞌkpa.  
\v 8 Ekpasiki ji á si re á lene jolo go njahmtahk nyi ekp'kpa elam alame, elkohn n'nehm ana ntahk nyehko. Solomon tob si elkohn etahk ana jio ka mmon no nkal no Fero no á ko-e go elbal.  
\v 9 Ntahk nyia kpee, bomo go elatahk tete song rehng egburu nlaaga, bomo nnahb ekahme rehng esi ekahme, bo ko atal nya nno a nno lim ab'lok enye, bo ko ntahme amahn kiimi, fere kpam es'song a njahm.  
\v 10 Bo ko agburu atal nya kpꞌsahb nꞌnob bum nnahb ekahme, atal nyandiki alab jo jolo ntahme enehkeni, nyandiki ntahme esehma.  
\v 11 Atal nya bo jo lang kunu o jolo atingi atal nya kpo kim kun, bo jo kiimi jol jang jang wane a nyako, bo tob kake agburu nti aseda nya elsiki.  
\v 12 Nlaaga nyi Ekpasiki, nlaaga nyi atahng etahk Esowo, a edi elsehnge yel ekp'kpa etahk Esowo, bele akahme nya bo ko atal nya bo soongo no lang. Go nkpake era anyehng anyehng bo jo kake ejangenti eseda. 
\s1 Huram Limi Eltum Etahk Esowo Aliibi 
\p  
\v 13 Ntula Solomon kehm tumu etib tv Huram go ejahbe ji bo kpo lung Taya re ba.  
\v 14 Nnyehn no Huram jolo nkalebun go et'tohngo ji Naftali, wo nde lohngo go Taya no jolo nne agb'gbe go eltum ebilekpi. Huram jolo nne egburu ngbere, no bele elkahne fere bel ekahnafem ji a á jo lim ntum abilikpi anehng anehng. Á ba goji ntula Solomon, fere ba lim eltum kpee ni bo ka-e re á lim. 
\p  
\v 15 Á ko ebilekpi mong ego na ebbal, ajehng ajehng elkul ero jolo ntahme ewubu kunu esi, ajok ego a l'ko nlehke gaare jolo ntahme enehkeni.  
\v 16 Á tob ko abilikpi lim esi ego ebbal re bo kunu go ero ago, esi ego ajehng jo wahre rehng ejum ntahme eni kunu esi.  
\v 17 Hiram ko agbekobo liibi asi ago ajehng ajehng nyao nya bo kunu ago, esi ego ajehng bi jo roomo ngbekobo esehma.  
\v 18 Á koo abilikpi lim nkpa akab pomegrenet\f + \fr 7:18 \ft epomegrenet foongo nkab eyabkpoko abehng fere jok ana nkab mehrekv\f* ebal nya bo kahne sennge agbekobo nyao liibi asi ago. Á limi ano esi ego ajehng ajehng.  
\v 19 Asi ago nya á limi kunu go ago nya edi eljehke ji alatahk, jolo go elfoongo ni at'tul nya ma nyange nya bo kpo lung re lili, wahre rehng ntahme eni.  
\v 20 Go asi ago nyao nya bo limi ana ekpeeke, go ego ebbal ebbal, kohlo agbekobo nya bo liibi no, o wo bo kunu akabe pomegrenet nya bo mongo no, atahl awubu nkpake ebal.  
\v 21 Huram lo ago nyao go edi eljehke ji alatahk, go mbuksong Etahk Esowo. Ego ji jolo ejang eboblum á lungu re Jakin, ji jolo go ejang ebobkal á lungu re Boaji.  
\v 22 Asi ago nya bo limi kunu jolo ana etˈtul ji ma nyange ji bo kpo lung re lili. Ano wo eltum ni ago male no.  
\v 23 Á nyane akuungu lim egburu ekpungkpung ji bo jo lung re agburu aya, kpange rehng ntahme eni kunu esi, fere wahre elkul ero rehng tahme enehkeni kunu esi. Á l'kak nlehke sennge, nlehke mio bahke labe rehng eltahl a ntahme erakera kunu esi.  
\v 24 Go nla nyi nkahl ero ekpungkpung, á mongo nsol ana abon mbahr. Á jo gaare eyakebo anyehng kehm mongo abon mbahr awubu. Ngare nyi bo nyane akuungu mong agburu aya wo bo tob mong abon mbahr.  
\v 25 Agburu aya kuumu go njahm ewubu a nfong ebal, nfong era sennge esamahr go ejang ebobkal, era sennge erede nfam, era sennge go ejang eboblum, era sennge go ero nfam. Agburu aya kuumu efong bio, bo kpee sennge asamahr ga elatahk, akpade ebo woomo go nla agburu aya jio.  
\v 26 Akpang nya nkahl ekpungkpung jio bahke rehnge ana akpang ndabbo, nkahl enye kpahle ana etu, ana et'tul ji ma nyange. Alahb bahke ma yel o rehng egalon atahl alon alon nkpel atahl alon a nkpel ewubu. (11,000).  
\v 27 Á tob ko abilikpi lim nkohl na ewubu nya bo kake agare elbannge go akpade, ajehng jo labe rehng ntahme eni, tob jolo ano go akpang, fere jol ntahme era go elkul ero.  
\v 28 Bo tob ko abilikpi lim elkohl kunu go akpakenti nya bele akpade.  
\v 29 Go agbaange enye bo fiki agabe lake o, a efong go aserubim. Go ero a nnahbandi nyi agabe a efong bio, bo kpe kak nliibi nyehko nyi bo ko abilikpi lim.  
\v 30 Elkohl anehng anehng bele ngbojok nyi kuumu go ekpade ebni, bo ko at'tuul liibi ejang abehng abehng.  
\v 31 Bele akahl nnyo ana nkpangennyo, nnyo eme jolo ejehngka fere kpange rehng ejum ntahme kunu esi. Bo fiki nsol nnyo eme. Nkohl ny'nehm yiimi songo songo bel agoongo, jolem bannge bannge ana etu.  
\v 32 Agare ani nyao jol akpekpe, akjehl nya agare nyao jolo o. Nne lˈkak nlehke gare ajehng fere tanne, bahke labe rehnge ejum ntahe ebal.  
\v 33 Agare nyao jolo ana agare mehtv akuungu, akjehl enye a nkehb go ahob, bo ko akuungu lim.  
\v 34 Elkohl anehng anehng jo bele edi ebjabbe na ebni, nya bo lake go nsongo elkohl eni eni.  
\v 35 Go ero elkohl nio bo kunu ekpake ekuungu ji jol ejennka sennge, bahke rahbe rehng ejang ekubit. Bo ko ejum jˈnehm lim agbaange enye a nnyo ekuungu mio.  
\v 36 Á fiki aserubim, a agabe, go nrahn mbohng go agbaange enye a nnyo mio. fere tahng nsol nyehko liibi akahl enye.  
\v 37 Ana wo Huram limi nkohl ewubu nyio, bo ko elkohn mmul anyehng lim, fvfo jolo elkohnkohn anehng.  
\v 38 Huram kehm koko ebilikpi lim ngbojok ewubu nyi bo bahke jo kunu nkohl agare nyio, ngbojok anyehng alahb bahke yele rehng egallon atahl awubu. A l'ko nlehke gare, bomo nkahl nnyoa ngbojok mio rehng anyohko, bahke rehnge ejum ntahme era.  
\v 39 Á bumu nkohl elon go ejang eboblum bi Etahk Esowo, elon nyehko go ejang ebobkal. Á bumu ekpungkpung jio go ejang eboblum, kohlo ejang ero nfam bi etahk Esowo.  
\v 40 Huram tob limi abon agbojok, a agburu aguremgbang, go nkpinsgi nyi bo jo kak alung madde. 
\p Ano wo Huram limi ntum kpee nyi a jo lim ka ntula Solomon go Etahk ji Jehova:  
\v 41 Ego ebbal; esi ego ebbal nya jolo ana abon agbojok go ero ago; nkpi agbekobo ebal nyi bo tahnge no liibi aro ago nyao nya li ana abon agbojok go ero ago;  
\v 42 Pomegrinati atahl tahl nya jolo ka nsol nyi bo tahnge liibi ago (nkpia pomegrinati ebal jolo ka nkpi agbekobo anyehng nyi bo roomo liibi esi ego ji jolo ana abon ngbojok go ero ago).  
\v 43 Nkohl ewubu nyi bo kake agare, a ngbojok ewubu ebo;  
\v 44 Ekpungkpung, a ewuba nfong ebal nyi woomo go nla;  
\v 45 atu, agburu aguremgbang, go nkpingi alung amadde. 
\p Nsol nyia kpee nyi Huram limi no ka ntula Solomon tib go etahk Jehova, bo ko abilikpi lim, nya bo ma dohk.  
\v 46 Ntul ka elkahn, bo ramme adi nya bo jo mong nsol nyio, go edi ebale bale ji Jodan, elka elka ni Sukoti a Jaretan.  
\v 47 Solomon jol nsol nyia kpee á dumem, tibre nsol jolo gbalee, jol bo maam dumu kahn ana lubu no.  
\v 48 Solomon tob limi nsol kpee nyi bo ko liibi Etahk Jehova: 
\p egudu njom ji agul, ekpˈkuru agul ji bo jo kunu ebred ji Esamahr bi Jehova;  
\v 49 Nti enyaale nyi bo ko nnyam nyam agul lim, (eblon go ejang eboblum, eblon nyehko ejang ebobkal go mbuksong nyi ekpˈkpa atahng); atˈtul agul a enyaale, go nliki agun nyi bo ko agul lim.  
\v 50 Nkpingi nyi bo ko nnyam nyam agul lim, afahnggba nya bo kpo ko soongo av enyaale, nkpingi alung amadde, nkpingi nyi bo jo kak insensa, ebil ji bo kpo kum jamme elgu mbu yiimi, nya jolo ka nkimi nyi atahng Edi ji Sahb lˈli Saang, tob jolo ka abutahk nya egburu ekp'kpa ji Etahk Esowo.  
\v 51 Eji eltum kpee ni Ntula Solomon jo lim go etahk Jehova ma mal, á kehm koko nsol kpee nyi David nde jabbe kak Esowo go ebo, asivla a agul, go nsol ekp'kpa aliibi, ba bum go ekp'kpa nsol akuuru go etahk Jehova. 
\c 8  
\s1 Bo Feere Elkohl Atahm Ba Go Etahk Esowo 
\p  
\v 1 Owo Ntula Solomon kehm kuku anebkul nfam ba Isreel, a atubesi kpee ba atꞌtohngo, go atubesi ane go ebangenahb ajehng ajehng, re bo rod elkohl nwongo nyi Jehova go Jayon ejahbe Devid ni ba a ni.  
\v 2 Aneblum ba Isreel kpee kehm bake ba kono edi ajehng goji ntula Solomon ngare nyi bo jo lim elkak abonkpatahk, go nnyahng Etanim mi jolo nnyahng esehma mi elya.  
\v 3 Ngare nyi anebkul ba Isreel kpee ma ba rehng, abalimajom kehm rodo elkohl nwongo,  
\v 4 fvfo bo rodo elkohl nwongo ni Jehova, a ebkpatahk elwane, a nsol elliibi enye kpee nyi li saang go atahng. Abalimajom a anebe etˈtohngo ji Levi kehm solo nsol nyio kpee,  
\v 5 ntula Solomon a anebe Isreel kpee ba jolo a ne, bo jo jene go esamahr elkohl nwongo, ko ejoro gbalee lim ajomjom, jol nne kpeem ma kahn nfange. 
\p  
\v 6 Owo abalimajom kehm koko elkohl nwongo ni Jehova ba a ni go edi ji bo limi ka-e go atahng ekpꞌkpa ji etahk Esowo, atahng nkimi nyi li saang, ba bum go nla nyi akpungkpung nya eserabim.  
\v 7 Akpungkpung Eserabim nyange konngo elkohl nwongo, fere tob bulu elkohl nwongo, a nti nyi bo jo ko sol.  
\v 8 Nti nyio labe sehng re nne bahke ma nyehn asi enye ga atahng ekpˈkpa etahk Esowo Edi Ji Li Saang, go elatahk nne nehm ma sa nyehn, tiki li o tete tub lela.  
\v 9 Ejumjum woomem go elkohl, sehngem akpataale abal nya Mosis kake no go Horeb, edi ji Jehova ko nwongo enye a anebe Isreel, ngare nyi bo jo lohng go Ijib.  
\v 10 Tvtv ana abalimajom lohngo go Edi Ji Li Saang, ekparesemsem kehm tahle ba bulu etahk ji Jehova.  
\v 11 Fvfo abalimajom maam kpe lim eltum ajom ebo tib ekparesemsem, tib ellub ni Jehova ebrur go ege Etahk. 
\p  
\v 12 Owo Solomon kehm bungu re, <<Jehova ebbung re á bahke woomo go nkom ejannge;  
\v 13 Etingitingi me n si egburu nobo nobo etahk ka-a, edi ji a bahke jolo go njinanjini.>> 
\p  
\v 14 Ana anebe Isreel kpee kpeka yim ona, ntula Solomon kehm sennge esamahr goji ane, kehm fuulu bo.  
\v 15 Owo á kehm bungu re: 
\p Eltehke jol ka Jehova Esowo bi anebe Isreel, ye ji ma ko abo enye lim enyam bi á nyame no tong Devid nsoo ewame re biingi go nseenge. Tib á bungu re,  
\v 16 <Bomo efung bi n yehke Isreel ane ebame go Ijib, n ka yehke ejahbe ajehng ajehng go etꞌtohngo Isreel, re bo si etahk ji bahke jo kpunu Mbing enyame, wo Devid wo m m-e yehke re á fili Isreel ane ebame.> 
\p  
\v 17 Devid nsoo ewame jol-e go ege eltim re á si etahk Esowo go Mbing nyi Jehova, Esowo bi Isreel.  
\v 18 Wo Jehova bungu tong nsoo ewame Devid re, <<Tib eji wob-a go eltim re wo si etahk Esowo ji bahke kpunu Mbing enyame, á limi sehng re wo bel ntir nyia go ega eltim.  
\v 19 Limi limi kan, wo sang bahke sehke Etahk Esowo jio, mmon ewa wo, ye ji li alung a ngubjing nyꞌnya, ye wo bahke sehke etahk Esowo jio ji bahke kpunu Mbing enyame.> 
\p  
\v 20 <<Jehova eblim ebbiingi ana á nyame no: Me n ji go eti etul ji nsoo ewame Devid, fvfo anv n jehk go eti etul ji Isreel, jang jang ana Jehova nyame no, me n si Etahk Esowo ji bahk kpunu Mbing nyi Jehova Esowo bi Isreel.  
\v 21 Me n toobo edi o ji elkohl nwongo nyi Jehova wob no, ji á limi no go esamahr babnso ewahre ngare nyi á yehke bo go Ijib.>> 
\s1 Ero Bi Solomon Kake No Rod Etahk Ka Esowo 
\p  
\v 22 Owo Solomon kehm mehle yiimi go mbuksong egudu njom ji bo kpo lim njom ka Jehova, go esamahr anebe Isreel kpee, nyange abo enye ton go ero,  
\v 23 kehm bungu re: 
\p Jehova Esowo bi Isreel, Esowo abehng abehng limm bi li ana wo go ero ejahbetul, afi ga ndi a atahng ndi, wo ji kpo bum nwongo nyi elkoro a alokeltum eba, bo ji kpo soro asi go ega abang a ntim a ntim ebo.  
\v 24 Wob bum enyame eba a nsoo Devid nlokeltum ewa, wob ko nnyo ema nyam enyam, fere ko abo enya lim enyam bio, ana li a lela. 
\p  
\v 25 Anv Jehova, Esowo bi Isreel, bum enyam eba bi a nyame ka Devid nsoo ewame, bi a bungu re, <A nehm tiki jol go elehng nne no bahke jehke go eti etul ji Isreel go egame esamahr, lꞌlub jol re abon eba bahke bele ekunukpu go nsol kpee nyi bo kpˈlimi, jo jen go agame esamahr, ana wo ma jen.>  
\v 26 Fvfo anv, Esowo bi Isreel, nong alum enya nya a nyame tong nsoo Devid nlokeltum ewa lohko jol ano go etingitingi. 
\p  
\v 27 Wo etingitingi ji re Esowo bahke jolo a njina? Ewuungu ji elbung, jol ejahbetul ji kpꞌsahb wꞌwahre, wa-a nehm ma biingi. Bahke limi renan etahk Esowo jia kehm-a biingi ji m ma si!  
\v 28 Limi limi kan, lub wuungu atung enya go ero bi nlokeltum ewa kpˈkake a elgboongo re wo tib-r ndon, Jehova Esowo ebame. Wuk eling a ero bi nlokeltum ewa kpꞌkake go ega esamahr lela.  
\v 29 Lub lennge amahr enya, wo seenge etahk jia atv a njul, edi jia ji a bungu re, <Mbing enyame bahke jolo o,> eji a bahke wuku ero bi nlokeltum ewa kpꞌkake seenge esamahr ebe edi jia.  
\v 30 Wuk elgboongo ni nlokeltum ewa, a ni Isreel ane eba, eji bo kpˈkake ero seenge edi jia. Wuk go ejahbetul edi ellene eja, a lꞌwuk tahm ka-r. 
\p  
\v 31 Nne lˈsoodo nnebjing ewe, wo lꞌjol re á bahke koko nwongo, á lꞌba ba ko nwongo go mbuksong egudu njom etahk Esowo jia,  
\v 32 wuk go ejahbetul, wo lim ejum. Lam alokeltum eba, ka nne no ma lim ejum jio ebi, wo nne no ki lim ebi, ka-e eno.  
\v 33 Ngare nyi ane eba, anebe Isreel, bo ma gbo go ebta go esamahr anebekv ebo, tib go ebo abiafem nya bo ma lim bade a na, bo lꞌfere sennge feere go ega, ba tehk mbing enya, jo kak ero fere jo gboongo go etahk Esowo jia,  
\v 34 tˈti lub wuk go ejahbetul, wo fere tahm ka Isreel ane eba go ebo abiafem, fere ko bo ba go ndi nyi a ka babnde abo. 
\p  
\v 35 Lꞌjol re elbung nehme kpe na elahb tib go esi abiafem nya ane eba ma lim bade a na, bo lꞌkak ero seenge go edi jia, fere tehk mbing enya, fere sennge njahm go ebo abꞌbi tib eji a ma kak bo erem,  
\v 36 tˈti wuk go ero, wo fere tahm ka Isreel alokeltum eba go ebo abiafem, Isreel ane eba. Tib bo mbang nyi nno ana bo bahke lene nkpin ebo, fere tum elahb tv go ndi nyi a ka ane eba ana ejum elehkelkv.  
\v 37 Ngare nyi egburu njal, afi abˈbi ayam lꞌba go ejahbe, afi akab nti wuudu fere bol, agohrobi afi akpaange, afi anebekv ba sennge bo kak go eboa nfam, elkohn elrannge anehng anehng a eyam abehng abehng bi bahke bake,  
\v 38 fvfo ngare anyehng anyehng nyi nnea Isreel lˈkak ero, afi gboongo, no nne fere kahn bade erem bi li no go ege eltim, fere nyange abo enye ton go etahk Esowo jia,  
\v 39 tˈti wuk go ejahbetul, edi ji wo lene no. Wo tahm ka bo, lim toono nne awohng awohng go mbang ana nyi á limi no, eji a kpꞌkahne eltim ene <<tib wo ntahngtahng kpꞌ kahne eltim ni ane kpee>>,  
\v 40 eji bo lꞌfahl-a ngare kpe kpe nyi bo lene go ndi nyi a ka babnso ewahre. 
\p  
\v 41 Go eyake ji ajenne ba ki lohng go Isreel ane eba, wo bo lohng go ajahbe nya li fee ba tib bob wuk bade egburu mbing enya-  
\v 42 tib ane bahke wuku bade egburu mbing enya, a egburu ebo eba, bi a ma tanne, - bo lˈba kak ero seenge esamahr etahk Esowo jia,  
\v 43 tˈti wuk go ejahbetul, edi ji a lene no,wo lim ajehng ajehng ji njenne lꞌbahb go ega, eji ane kpee ba li go njini lꞌkahn mbing enya, fere jo fahl-a, ana ane eba Isreel kpo fahl-a, bo bahke tob kahn re etahk jia ji m ma si, Mbing enya li o. 
\p  
\v 44 Ane eba lꞌlohng je re bo song nok a anebekv ebo, edi ajehng ajehng ji a lꞌtum bo, fvfo bo lꞌkak ero ka Jehova, seenge go ejahbe jia ji a ma yehke, a etahk Esowo ji m ma si tib Mbing enya.  
\v 45 Tˈti wuk ero ebo go ejahbetul, a elgboongo ebo, wo lim ji bo kpˈsebe.  
\v 46 Ngare nyi bo lꞌlim abiafem bade a na- tib nnene limm no kil jo lim abiafem- a fere bel erakatahng a bo, fere rod bo ka anebekv, bo ji bahke rodo bo ana aju tahm go ebo ejahbe, jolo fee afi kpidikpidi;  
\v 47 Fvfo bo lꞌfere gbo ndon yaange ntir abo go ndi nyi bo wob eju, fere gbo ndon, gboong-a seenge go ndi nyi ane ba bobo bo kak eju, fere bung re, <Wahr eblim abiafem, wahr eblim ebi, ji e ma lim ebsab sehng>;  
\v 48 fvfo bo lꞌsennge feere go ega a ntim a ntim ebo, a atohko atohko ebo, go ejahbe ji anebekv ba ko bo ba kak eju, fere kak ero seenge go ndi nyia nyi a ka babnde ebo, fere feere go ejahbe ji a ma yehke, a Etahk Esowo ji m ma si go ega-a Mbing;  
\v 49 Tˈti wuk go ejahbetul, edi ji a lene no, wo lim ji bo kpˈsebe.  
\v 50 Fvfo tahm ka ane eba, ba ma lim abiafem bada na; tahm ka bo go abi nsol nya bo ma-a soodo, wo tob lim ane ba bobo bo go ebta nyehn bo ndon;  
\v 51 tibre bo ane eba ba, a ejum elehkelkv eja, bo ji a yehke bo go Ijib, go edi jio ji nfuubu erem. 
\p  
\v 52 Nong amahr enya lennge wo wuk elgboongo ni nlokeltum ewa, a elgboongo ni Isreel ane eba kpꞌgboongo, fvfo jo wuk bo ngare anyehng anyehng nyi bo lꞌling tob-a.  
\v 53 Tib a jahme bo ebo go ellong ajahbe njini kpee re bo jol ejum elehkelkv jꞌja, ana a bungu gbul gbul gbuul sehng eji Mosis nlokeltum ewa, eji wo Nsoo Ntula Jehova yehke babnsoo ebahre go Ijib.>> 
\p  
\v 54 Eji Solomon ma kak aro nyaa kpee mal fere gboongo Jehova, á kehm mehle go mbuksong egudu njom ji Jehova, edi ji á jolo go alahng ajamme, fere ton abo enye go ejahbetul Esowo.  
\v 55 Á mehle yiimi, kehm fuulu anebe Isreel kpee ba jolo o, kehm bungu wahre wahre re: 
\p  
\v 56 Nong eltehke jol ka Jehova, ye ji ma ka Isreel ane ebe erekekv ana á nyame no. Jol ellum anehng anehng ka kane go anobo nobo anyam kpee nya á nyame no sehng goji Mosis nlokeltum ewe.  
\v 57 Nong Jehova Esowo ebahre jol anahre, ana á jolo a babnsoo ewahre; nong á ki-r tiki yake abo, afi fere ten-r.  
\v 58 Nong á sennge ntim enyahre tv elne, eji e lꞌjo jen go egea mbang, fere jo bum nkahn, atahm, a ntibi enye, nya á ka babnsoo ewahre.  
\v 59 Fvfo nong alum enyame nyaa, nya m ma kak ero go esamahr bi Jehova, jol bad bad goji Jehova Esowo ebahre atv a njul, eji á lꞌlim ji nlokeltum ewe kpꞌsebe, a ji ane ebe Isreel kpꞌsebe efung abehng abehng,  
\v 60 eji ane kpee ba li go njini lꞌkahn re Jehova Esowo bi, fvfo Esowo bindiki go kpeem li.  
\v 61 Fvfo nong ntim enyahne kpee jol ka Jehova Esowo ebahre, wahn jo toono ntibi enye, fere jo kpunu nkahn enye ana ń kpˈlimi lela. 
\s1 Bo Rodo Etahk Esowo Kak Jehova go Ebo 
\p  
\v 62 Owo ntula Solomon a anebe Isreel kpee kehm limi ajomjom go esamahr bi Jehova.  
\v 63 Solomon ko efong atahltahl nkpel atahl abal a nkpel elku (22000) fere ko ejoro a ebul atahltahl nkpela atahlku (120000) lim njom nyi elkoono. Ano ntul a anebe Isreel kpee faake etahk Esowo jio ka Jehova.  
\v 64 Efung bꞌnehm o, ntul rodo elka nlaaga, go mbuksong mi etahk Jehova fere lim jol saang, owo á limi ajom nya eljahme fi, a nya nkohl, a afom nnyam ma njom elkoono, tibre egudu njom ebilikpi ji jolo go esamahr bi Jehova se sehng, re bo ko lim ajom nya eljahme fi, a nya nkohl, a afom nnyam ma njom elkoono. 
\p  
\v 65 Ano wo Solomon limi Elkak ni Nkpatahk nyio kpee ngare nyia, anebe Isreel fvfo kpee jolo a ne, nrur ane gbalee, ane ba lohng go Lebo ji Hamati tete song rehng fee edamme ji Ijib. Bo limi eyiiki jia go esamahr bi Jehova Esowo ebahre go nfung na esehma, kpe budu nfung esehma nyehko, kpee jolo ewubu a nfung eni.  
\v 66 Eji elkak ma mal, etoono efung, bi biingi nfung enehkeni, á tongo ane feere kehnge go eboa ntahk. Bo kake ntul saam, fere mehl kehnge go eyebatahng, a elgeere go ebo a ntim, go anoobo nsol kpee nya Jehova ma lim ka nlokeltum ewe Devid a Isreel ane ebe. 
\c 9  
\s1 Jehova kehm lohngo ba kpiri Solomon 
\p  
\v 1 Ngare nyi Solomon ma si etahk Jehova mal, a ekpasiki ntul, fvfo lim nsol kpee nyi á sebe re á lim.  
\v 2 Owo Jehova kehm lohngo ba kpir-e go etoono nkpele, ana á tohk-e kpiri go Gibion.  
\v 3 Jehova kehm-e tongo re, <<Me n wuk ero eba, a elgboongo ni a ma gboongo go egame esamahr; me n lim etahk Esowo ji a ma si re jol saang, eji a ma kak Mbing enyame o go njinanjini. Amahr enyame a eltim ename bahke jolo o ngare kpe kpe. 
\p  
\v 4 Go ejang bꞌba, wo lꞌfere toon-m a eltim eltim ena kpee, a etingitingi, ana nso Devid jo toon-m, fere jo lim elkahn anehng anehng ni n ka-a no, jo toono ntibi, a atahm,  
\v 5 m bahke jehke ebangenahb eja go eti etul ji Isreel go njinanjini, ana n nyame tong nso Devid eji m bungu re, <A nehm tiki jol elehng nne no bahke jehke go nji etul nyi Isreel.> 
\p  
\v 6 Wo lˈfere jol wo, afi etˈtohngo eja, lꞌsenng-m njahm, fere ten eltoono nkahn a ntibi nyi m ma-n ka fere tahm song loko asowo nyako, fere jo kak bo,  
\v 7 owo m bahke yabe anebe Isreel go ndi nyi m ma ka bo, fvfo m bahke tene etahk ji m ma lim re jol saang ka mbing enyame. Isreel bahke jolo na jol ejum elgal, fere jol ejum enyok go ellong ajahbe kpee.  
\v 8 Etahk jia ji li saang, bahke jolo ana ebimbim, bahke jolo ejum ji bahke tane ane ba kpꞌsehnge go mbang eko, bo fere jo nyok re, <Jenji wahnge Jehova ma lim elkohn ejum ana jia bada ndi nyia, a Etahk Esowo jia ji li saang?>  
\v 9 Ane bahke faange re, <Tibre bobten Jehova Esowo ebo, ye ji yehke babnde ebo go ndi nyi Ijib, fere kpi asowo nyako toono, jo loko, fere jo kak bo, owo wahnge Jehova ma ko elrannge nia ba kunu bo go esi.> >> 
\s1 Ntum nyehko Nyi Solomon Limi No 
\p  
\v 10 Eji nnya eltahl ma mal nyi Solomon ko no si ntahk ebal ebal nyia, etahk Esowo ji Jehova, a ekpasiki eje,  
\v 11 ntula Solomon kaa Hiram ntula Taya esi ejahbe eltahl, nya li go Galili, tib Hiram wo ka-e nti aseda, a nti junipa, go agul nya á jo seb re á ko jo lim eltum.  
\v 12 Wo eji Hiram lohngo go Taya re á ba nyehn asi ajahbe nya Solomon ka-e no, asi ajahbe nyao we-e korem.  
\v 13 Á kehm-e bahbe re, <<Elkohn asi ajahbe a nya a nya a ma-m ka, mmonannee? Á kehm lungu asi ajahbe nyao re Kabul\f + \fr 9:13 \ft Kabul: ji lohngo re, lohngem ejum\f* (ji lohngo re, lohngem ejumjum), mbing nyio nyi bo kpi no tete tub lela.  
\v 14 Limi limi kan Hiram ebtum ebahk agul atahltahl nkpel ewubbal a atahl awubu tv ntula Solomon.  
\v 15 Ntoora nnyo nyia li bade ntum nyi ntula Solomon jo bob ane kak bo jo lim atahntahn ntum, re bo si etahk Esowo ji Jehova a ekpasiki eje, a ndi nyi á kake adamme, a akahme nya Jeusalem, re bo tuungu esi ejahbe Hajo, a Megido go Gejer si.  
\v 16 Re kehm rehnge ngare nyio Fero ntula Ijib ebba bohko Gejer ebta, fere bob Gejer. Fere jahm agun. Á wulu anebe Kenan ba lene o, fere rod ka mmon ewe no nkal ana ejum ayare elbal mmon, ngare nyi mmon no nkal song bal Solomon.  
\v 17 Solomon tuungu Gejer si. Á si Beti Heron ji edamme,  
\v 18 Baalati a Tadmor ji li go edi erikendi ji li wum wum, go egea ndi,  
\v 19 a ajahbe enye nya á jo kuuru nsol, a ajahbe nya amvtv akuungu enye, a anyꞌnya enye, a ejum ajehng ajehng ji jo kor-e re á si go Jeusalem, a Lebanon a adi kpee nya á jo fili.  
\v 20 Ane kpe tiki jol o ba lohng go Amor, a anebe Hiti, a anebe Periji, a anebe Hivi, go anebe Jebusi ba lene o ndi nyio. Fvfo ane baa anebe Isreel sang.  
\v 21 Etˈtohngo ji ane bao ba sa o go ndi nyio, bo ji anebe Isreel ki kam bo yehke, bo ba jolo ane ba Solomon jo bob bo, bo jo lim ntum eju ka-e, ano wo li no tete rehng efung bi lela.  
\v 22 Wo Solomon tikem ko nnea Isreel bum eju; bo jolo abanoko ebta, ane ba jo lim eltum a ne, atubesi ane, atubesi nsoja, a ane ba jo fili amvtv akuungu, a ane ba jo fing.  
\v 23 Bo jˈnehm ba tob jol atubesi go eltum anehng anehng ni Solomon bele no, ane atahltahl atahl asehma ane awubu, atubesi baa ba jo kpur fere jo tv ane ba jo lim eltum.  
\v 24 Eji mmona Fero no nkal ma lohng go ejahbe ji Devid ba rehng go ekpasiki ji Solomon ma si ka-e, á kehm kake ndi go adamme nyao.  
\v 25 Nkpel era go elya Solomon jo limi njom nyi eljahme fi, a njom nyi elkoono go egudu njom ji á ma si ka Jehova, jo kak agun go insen go esamahr bi Jehova jo teebe, mbang nyia, á jo limi ji jolo ka-e re á lim go etahk Esowo.  
\v 26 Ntula Solomon tob kono asohkkahng go Ejion Geber, ji li kohlo Elati ji Edom go nkpe Aya Nkpafa.  
\v 27 Owo Hiram kehm tumu ane ebe, ba kpo jen agburu aya, bo ji kpꞌkahne ana aya li no, re bo jo fing asohkkahng a ane ba Solomon.  
\v 28 Bo fingi asohkkahng rehng go Ofir, fere song ko abahk agul nya a lˈdumu bahke lubu rehng ebam akang atahltahl nkpela atahlku ba ka ntula Solomon. 
\c 10  
\s1 Ntula Nnenkal no lohng go Seba Ba Yele Solomon Eljen 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ntula nnenkal no Seba wuku bade elgahm ni Solomon, ni ko ekpunu ba ka mbing nyi Jehova, á ba re, á ba wuungu Solomon a atahntahn abahbe.  
\v 2 Eji á ba rehng go Jeusalem a ellong ane gbalee, a nsol afang gbalee, akamel gbalee solo nkang, agul gbalee, go anobonobo atal, nya sahb kˈkim ekun á ba goji Solomon, kehm ba bung bada nsol kpee nyi wob-e go ege atahng.  
\v 3 Solomon faange abahbe enye kpee; ejumjum jolem ji sahb rꞌriidi ntula Solomon re á lennge ka-e.  
\v 4 Eji ntula nnenkal no Seba nyehne ngbere nyi Solomon a ekpasiki ji á ma si,  
\v 5 nsol alehke nyi kun-e go ekpukuru, ana abalimi eltum ebe kpo ji, ane ba kpo lok-e a nsol nyi bo kake go ngubjing, ane ba kpo fa amahm ka ntul, a ajom nya á kpo jahm fi go etahk ji Jehova, tan-e eko.  
\v 6 Á kehm bungu tong ntul re, <<Nsol nyi a ma lim, nyi n wuku go egame ejahbe, a ngbere enya lohko li go nseenge.  
\v 7 Wo n taamem nsol nyia tete n lohng ba, ba nyehn go egame amahr antahng. Go etingitingi, jol bo me-e tongem rehng ejang nsol nyi m ma ba nyehn, go ngbere a afang, a kpi gbalee sehnge ana n wuku no.  
\v 8 Nyehn egburu eyebatahng ji ane eba bahke bele! Nyehn egburu eyebatahng ji abalimeltum eba bahke bele! bo ji bahke soro asi jo yiimi go ega esamahr jo wuk ngbere enya!  
\v 9 Eltehke jol ka Jehova Esowo eba, ye ji me-e yebe atahng tob-a re á jehk-a go eti etul ji Isreel. Tib go esi elkoro ni Jehova kpi nkahlkahl ka Isreel, á ma-a kunu etul, eji á lˈjo lam elam ji nno, fere jo lim nsol nyi kpꞌnobo.>>  
\v 10 Á kehm kake ntul ebahk agul nya a lˈdumu lubu sehnge ebam akang atahltahl nkpele ewubu, a nsol nkang gbalee nyi kpo lim nsol yebe. Go atal nya nno a nno nya kpo sahb kˈkim ekun. Nnene kpeem tiki ko nkang gbalee nyi kpo lim nsol alehke yebe ana nyi ntula Seba ko ba ka ntula Solomon.  
\v 11 (Ellong asohkkahng nya Hiram ko agul go Ofer ba; fvfo bo tob ko nti gbalee nyi bo kpo lung re almug, a atal nya nno.  
\v 12 Ntula Solomon ko nti almug liibi Etahk Esowo a ekpasiki ntul, fere tob lim egehmegehme a egili ka abayimase. Wo elkohn nti almug nyaa bo ka kpe tiki ko ba go Isreel, jol elkohn nia bo ka kpe tiki nyehn bomo efung bio.  
\v 13 Ntula Solomon ka ntula nnenkal no Seba nsol kpee nyi á sebe no fere bahb, nsol nyehko nyi Solomon tohk-e kak go ege ebo wobem go atahng ellong nsol nyia. Owo á kehm feere a ane ebe kehnge go ege ejahbe. 
\s1 Afang nya Solomon 
\p  
\v 14 Agul nya Solomon jo bel elya elya jo lubu rehng ebam akang atahltahk atahl awubu.  
\v 15 Akpohko nya á jo ko goji abagungu nsol a abajenare woomem go atahng, a nya lohngo go abo nya Atul anebe Arab, a abafiladi ba ndi nyi Isreel.  
\v 16 Ntula Solomon limi ekum agul agul, atahl awubu nya nnen nya bo dv na. Kariki jol lubu rehnge ekilo agul ebsehma.  
\v 17 Ntula Solomon tob limi abonsˈsohko akum agul atahlku nya bo ma dv, sa ntiil ekum ajehng ajehng jo lub ana ekilo agul ebbal. Á kake nsol nyia go ekpasiki ntul go ekulegbe Lebanon.  
\v 18 Ntul fvfo tob limi egburu eti etul, bo ko ntang njok lim, fere ko agul nya nno wohng bulu.  
\v 19 Eti etul jio bele egudu elwahre na ebrakera, ero ebe bele ejehngka. Go ejang ebbal ebbal bi eti etul jio, bele edi ekunabo ji ntul bahke jo kunu abo, bo fiki egabe ji yim no ejang ebbal ebbal.  
\v 20 Eti etul kpi ngbahk erakera nyi nne bahke wahre rehng ero, ewubu egabe ebbal yim esi ngbahk ejang ebbal ebbal. Elkohn eti etul ana jia bo ka lꞌlim ka etul abehng abehng go njini.  
\v 21 Ntuku kpee nyi ntula Solomon jo wo alahb, bo limi go agul, a nsol nyi bo limi go ege Ekpasiki ekulegbe ji Lebanon bo ko agul nya nno a nno lim. Ejum ajehng ajehng bo koom asilva lim, tibre asilva ngare nyi Solomon ellub anehng anehng belem.  
\v 22 Ntul bele asohkkahng gbalee nya jo jen are, go aya ngare nyꞌnehm a asohkkahng nya Hiram. Asohk kahng nyao jo feere nkpel anyehng go nnya era, bo jo solo agul, asilva, ivori, a ebuk, go ellong nki. 
\p  
\v 23 Ntula Solomon gboo afang sehng, a ngbere sehnge atul bako kpee go njini.  
\v 24 Nne kpee go njini jo lohngo ba re bo ba wuk ngbere nyi Esowo ma kak Solomon go eltim.  
\v 25 Go elya elya, nne awohng awohng no lꞌba go ege, á jo ko ayare asilva, agul, abomo, nsol ebta, nsol nkang nyi kpo lim nsol alehke yebe, anyˈnya, a ebvankang.  
\v 26 Solomon bele amvtv akuungu, anyˈnya, á bele amvtv akuungu atahl tahkl nkpel era atahl awubu, a anyˈnya, atahl tahl go eltahl a nkpel ewubu nya á bumu go ejahbe amvtv akuungu, a nya jolo a ne go Jeusalem.  
\v 27 Ntul limi asilva jol ndaange ejum go Jeusalem ana atal, fvfo aseda jolo go nrur are akuntaake afik ekulegbe nya abangenahb awong.  
\v 28 Bo jo gunu anyꞌnya nya Solomon go Ijib, a Silisia, abajenare ntul jo gunu bo go Silisia, go ekun bi nno  
\v 29 Bo gungu amvtv akuungu go Ijib, go esekel asilva atahlatahl atahl awubu, anyꞌnya bo gunu go abahk asilva atahl asehma ebahk ebwubu. Bo tob tumu bo tv atul ba anebe Hiti, go atul ba anebe Aram. 
\c 11  
\s1 Ellong akal ba Solomon 
\p  
\v 1 Ntula Solomon bele elkoro a anebkal ajahmjahm gbalee, budu mmona Fero no nkal, á tob ko anebkal go Moab, ko go a Amon, ko go Edom, ko go Sidon, a go Hiti.  
\v 2 Bo lohng go ajahbe nya Jehova ma tong anebe Isreel re, <<Kana tiki ko elbal semme a bo, tibre bo bahke tiki sennge ntim enyahne feere goji asowo ebo.>> Wo Solomon tiki tub bo ejahm go ege elkoro.  
\v 3 Solomon bele akal atahltahl atahlku bo jolo abon ntul, nkoro enye jolo atahlku. Akal ebe senng-e eltim á jo toono asowo ebo.  
\v 4 Ngare nyi Solomon ma kul, akal ebe senng-e eltim feere goji asowo nyako, eltim ene kpeem jol kpe kpe, ejang bi Jehova Esowo ebe, ana eltim nde Devid jolo no.  
\v 5 Á jo toono Astoreti esowo nnenkal bi anebe Sidon kpo kak, a Molek ebꞌbi esowo bi anebe Amon.  
\v 6 Ano wo Solomon limi abiafem go esamahr bi Jehova, á toonem Esowo jang jang, ana Devid nde jo toon-e. 
\p  
\v 7 Go ewong ji ero nfam bi Jeusalem, Solomon song si etahk elom ka Semosi ebꞌbi esowo bi anebe Moab, a edi ji Molek ebi esowo bi anebe Amon.  
\v 8 Solomon limi akahnlom ka akal ebe kpee ba jolo ajahmjahm, bo jo jahm insen fi, fere jo lim ajom ka asowo ebo. 
\p  
\v 9 Wo Jehova atahng kehm-e rake tob Solomon tibre yeb yehke eltim ene goji Jehova Esowo bi Isreel, ye ji ma lohng ba kpiri nkpel na ebal.  
\v 10 Jol eji á ma tohko tong Solomon re á kꞌtoono asowo yako, Solomon kpunem elkahn ni Jehova.  
\v 11 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Solomon re, <<Eji li re ana so a kpˈlimi, fere ten elbumu nwongo enyame a ntibi enyame, m bahke tiki taare eti etul jia go ega ebo, fere song ka nlokeltum ewa go ellong alokeltum eba.  
\v 12 Jol eji li li ano, tib go esi ji nso Devid, n nehm lim go ngare nyi a kpeke li go elkpin. M bahke yehke go ebo bi mmon ewa.  
\v 13 Fvfo n nehm taare etul bio kpee go ege abo, m bahk-e kake etˈtohngo ajehng tib go esi ji Devid nlokeltum ewame, a esi ji Jeusalem ji m ma yehke.>> 
\s1 Anebekv Solomon 
\p  
\v 14 Owo Jehova kehm melle nnekv re á nok a Solomon, Hadad ji lohng go ebangenahb ntula Edom.  
\v 15 Mahne eji Devid jo nok ebta a Edom, Joab ji ntubesia nsoja, je re á song kpa akvne kak, wulu aneblum kpee go Edom.  
\v 16 Joab a anebe Isreel kpee jolo o go nnyahng erakera, tete bo rannge aneblum kpee go Edom.  
\v 17 Wo Hadad ngare nyia kpeka li mmonse, á be tahm go Ijib a egom atubesi ane ba anebe Edom, bo ji ma tohko loko nde.  
\v 18 Bo mehle go Media, tahm go Paran, owo bo ko ane go Paran tahm a bo, bo song rehng go Ijib goji ntula Fero, fvfo ye wo ka Hadad etahk, fere tob ka-e ndi, a nsol alehke.  
\v 19 Fero atahng jo yebe sehng tob Hadad, owo wahngka á ka-e mmonannyehn nkal ewe, ntula nnenkal Tapenesi go elbal.  
\v 20 Mmonannyehna Tapenesi no nkal, jele mmon no nlum ka-e no bo jo lung-e re, Genubati, fvfo ye wo Tapenesi le-e no go etahk ntul. Owo Genubati lene no go ellong abone Fero.  
\v 21 Eji Hadad jolo go Ijib, á kehm wuku re Devid ebtahm ebim ejok, fvfo re Joab ntubesi nsoja ebtob kpo. Owo Hadad kehm tongo Fero re, <<Yak-m, me n tahm feere song go egame ejahbe.>> 
\p  
\v 22 Fero kehm-e bahbe re, <<Wobjol go elehng ejum ajii <a,> ji wahnge a yahke feere go ega ejahbe?>> 
\p Hadad kehm faange re, <<Ejumjum, yak-m me n song!>> 
\p  
\v 23 Esowo tob melle Rejon mmon no Eliada, re á ba nok a Solomon. Rejon wo be goji nde nju, Hadadeje ji jolo ntula Joba.  
\v 24 Ngare nyi Devid rannge nsoja nyi Joba, Rejon koo ellong ane, bo ji ki jo wuk nyi etung, ye jol ntubesi abo. Atahnsi ane baa mehle song rehng go Damaskusi, go wo bo kak elsi ji jo fili ane.  
\v 25 Rejon jolo nnekv no anebe Isreel go afung kpee nya Solomon jolo go elkpin. Budu a atongtong nya Hadad jo lim. Rejon jo fili ane go Aram, fere jo bib a anebe Isreel. 
\s1 Jeroboam Tene Eltoono Solomon 
\p  
\v 26 Fvfo Jeroboam mmona Nebati kehm kpe sennge jo nok a ntul. Á jolo nlokeltum awohng go ellong alokeltum Solomon, nnea Efriim no lohng go Jereda, nnyehn jolo nkalebun no bo jo lung-e re Jerua.  
\v 27 Ntoora nnyo mi a ana á noko a ntul: Solomon ebkak ndi go adamme, fere tuungu akahme nya jolo sennge Jeusalem kak, ejahbe ji nde Devid.  
\v 28 Jeroboam jia jolo nnooba nne, fvfo eji Solomon nyehne ana njangkun nyia limi eltum ene, á kake re á jol ntubesi no ane ba kpo lim atahntahn ntum go etꞌtohngo ji Josef.  
\v 29 Ngare anyehng eji Jeroboam lohngo go Jeusalem asongo, owo Ahija nnyehnamahr no Silo kehm ba wan-e go mbang nyi abon ajahbe ki jol, á kake ekpawobo ji nfenfe. Bo bo ba jolo go elka emahng,  
\v 30 owo Ahija kehm jabbe ekpawobo ji á kake no, kehm yange wubu ejang elbal.  
\v 31 Owo á kehm bungu tong Jeroboam re, <<Rod ejang ebwubu bꞌba, tib ji Jehova Esowo bi Isreel ma bung ji a re, <Nyehnee!, m bahke yange eti etul jia go ebo bi Solomon, fere ka-a etꞌtohngo na ebwubu.  
\v 32 Wo tib go esi ji Devid nlokeltum ewame, a Jeusalem, ji m ma yehke go atꞌtohngo nya Isreel kpee, á bahke bele etꞌtohngo ajehng.  
\v 33 M bahke limi jia tibre Solomon a ane ebe bo ma-m ten, kpꞌfere kake Astoreti, esowo nnenkal bi anebe Sodon, a Kemosi esowo bi anebe Moab, a Molek esowo bi anebe Amon, fvfo bobten eljene go egama abang, fere ten eblimi ji kpꞌnobo go egame amahr, ntibi enyame a atahm bobten elbumu ana Devid nde no Solomon bumu no.  
\v 34 Wo n nehm yehke eti etul jia kpee go ebo bi Solomon; Me-e lim re á jol ntul go afung kpee nya á li elkpin, tib go esi ji Devid nlokeltum ewame, ye ji n yehk-e no, fvfo ye ji jo bum atahm enyame a ntibi.  
\v 35 M bahke yehke eti etul jia go ebo mmon ewe, fere ka-a etꞌtohngo ebwubu.  
\v 36 Wo m bahke kake mmona Solomon etꞌtohngo ajehng, eji ebangenahb ji Devid nlokeltum ewame bahke tiki jo bel ntul go egame esamahr go Jeusalem, go ejahbe ji n yehke re me n kak Mbing enyame.  
\v 37 Limi limi kan, tib wo, m bahk-a koko, a bahke fili ane kpee ba eltim ena kpꞌsebe; a bahke jolo ntul no Isreel.  
\v 38 A lꞌlim ajehng ajehng ji n ka-a elkahn, fere jen go egame abang, fere lim nsol nyi kpꞌnobo go egame esamahr, go elbumu ntibi enyame, a nkahn, ana Devid nlokeltum ewame jo bum, m bahke jolo a na. M bahke limi eti etul ka-a ji bahke kange ana ji n limi ka Devid, fvfo m bahk-a kake nfam nyi Isreel a jo fili.  
\v 39 M bahke kake etˈtohngo ji Devid erem tib go esi jia, wo n nehm kak bo erem go njinanjini.>>> 
\p  
\v 40 Solomon gare ana á bahke wulu Jeroboam, wo Jeroboam be tahm go Ijib goji Sisak ntul no Ijib, fere song jol go tete Solomon kpo. 
\s1 Elkv ni Solomon 
\p  
\v 41 Bade nsol nyehko kpee ana Solomon fili ejahbe - nsol kpee nyi á limi no, a ngbere nyi á tibi no bo nyono kak go nwer aka nyi atula Solomon  
\v 42 Solomon jolo go Jeusalem jo fili Isreel kpee go nnya atahl abal.  
\v 43 Owo Solomon kehm tahme ebim ejok, bo song kpa-e kak go ejahbe ji nde Devid. Rehoboam mmon ewe wo kuumu etul toon-e. 
\c 12  
\s1 Anebe Isreel Tene Eltoono Rehoboam 
\p  
\v 1 Rehoboam tahme go Sekem, edi ji Isreel kpee ma ji re bo bob-e etul.  
\v 2 Eji Jeroboam mmona Nebati wuku ana, (á tiki kpe jol go Ijib ana á be go esamahr bi ntula Solomon), á kehm lohngo go Ijib feere kehnge.  
\v 3 Bo kehm tumu re bo song lung Jeroboam ba, owo ye a anebe Isreel kpee kehm tahme goji Rehoboam kehm song bung tong-e re:  
\v 4 <<Nso si-r egburu elsol ni nlen, anv lim atahntahn ntum nyaa, a egburu elsol ni á si-r no fere yaare, wahr bahk-a loko.>> 
\p  
\v 5 Rehoboam kehm faange re, <<Feeren song go nfung era wahn feere ba go egame.>> Ano wo ane feere no.  
\v 6 Owo ntula Rehoboam kehm song kpiri anebkul mfam ba ma loko nde Solomon ngare nyi á jolo elkpin. Rohoboam kehm bahbe bo re, <<Elle ani ḿ bahk-m tubu ni m bahke faange ane baa?>> 
\p  
\v 7 Bo kehm-e faange re, <<Lꞌfere jol lela re á bahke jolo nlokeltum ka ane baa, fere loko bo, fvfo ka bo nfaange nyi bahke koro bo, bo bahke soro asi jol alokeltum eba ngare kpe kpe.>>  
\v 8 Wo Rehoboam tꞌten elle ni anebkul ka-e no, fere song kpiri atem ba bo tahme eljini ano, bo ji jo lok-e.  
\v 9 Á kehm bahbe bo re, <<Elle ani ḿ bahk-m tubu? Anv e bahke faange ane baa ba kp-m tongo re, <Lim elsol enahre yaare ni nso sii-r no.>?>> 
\p  
\v 10 Ajangkun nya bo tahme eljini ano kehm faange re, << Ane baa ma tong re, <Nso si-r egburu elsol, wo lub lim elsol enahre yaare> tong bo re, <Ebnyohkobo ebame kpꞌlubu sehnge ebun ji nsoo.>  
\v 11 Nsoo jo si-n alublub nsol; m bahke limi kpe lub na budu; Nsoo jo dv-n go ntii; wo me m bahke jo ko anang jo ta-n.>> > 
\p  
\v 12 Eji ma rehng nfung era, owo Jeroboam a ane kpee kehm feere ba goji ntula Rehoboam ana á bungu no re, <<Feeren ba go egame nfung era lꞌsehng.>>  
\v 13 Ntul faange ane baa egban egban. Á tene elle ni anebkul tub-e no,  
\v 14 fere toono elle ni ajangkun nya bo tahme eljini ano, bungu re, <<Nsoo si-n elsol ni nlen; m bahke limi kpe lub na budu. Nsoo dv-n go ntii, wo me m bahke jo ko nnang jo ta-n.  
\v 15 Ano wo ntul ki wuungu ane atung, tibre ejum ji limi a lohng go ebo bi Jehova, eji lˈlim biingi ellum ni Jehova ni á bungu tong Jeroboam mmona Nebati, sehng go nnyo mi Ahija nnea Silo. 
\p  
\v 16 Eji anebe Isreel kpee nyehne re ntul wuungem bo atung, bo kehm faange ntul re: 
\p <<Wo anv mbake anyii e kpi kpi goji Devid, ebo abii e kpi kpi goji mmona Jesi? 
\p Wahn anebe Isreel, Feeren go egahna nkpatahk! Song kpur-n etahk ejahne, wahn Devid!>> 
\p Ano wo anebe Isreel kehm tahme kehnge.  
\v 17 Wo bade anebe Isreel ba jolo go ajahbe Juda, Rehoboam tiki jo fili bo. 
\p  
\v 18 Ntula Rehoboam kehm tumu Adoniram, ye ji jolo ntubesi no ane ba jo lim atahntahn ntum, wo Isreel kpee tuub-e atal wul. Wo ntula Rehoboam noko be kuumu go mmvtv akuungu enye, be for song rehng go Jeusalem.  
\v 19 Ano wo anebe Isreel tiki kpe li ekv a ebangenahb ji Devid tete tub lela.  
\v 20 Eji anebe Isreel kpee wuku re Jeroboam ebfeere kehnge, bo kehm tumu, bo lung-e ba ga edi ji ane ma kono, bo fere bob-e ntul no Isreel kpee. Etˈtohngo ji Juda ji ji sa no jo toono ebangenahb ji Devid.  
\v 21 Ngare nyi Rehoboam ba rehng go Jeusalem, á kehm ba lung etꞌtohngo ji Juda a etˈtohngo ji Benjamin kpee, ane atahltahl nkpel atahl abal ewubu ba kpo nok abohng, re bo nok ebta a etꞌtohngo ji Isreel, fere ko eti etul jia ka Rehoboam mmona Solomon. 
\p  
\v 22 Wo Esowo kehm bungu tong nnyehnamahr Esowo re:  
\v 23 Tong Rehoboam mmona Solomon ntula Juda, a anebe Juda go anebe Benjamin kpee, a erik ane bako re,  
\v 24 <Ejum ji a ji Jehova bungu no re: Kana je song nok a abonane ebahne, anebe Isreel. Feeren kehnge, wahn ane kpee, ji kpˈjolo a, me wo kpˈlimi.>>> Ano wo bo kpunu ellum ni Jehova, kehm feere kehnge ana Jehova kaa bo elkahn. 
\s1 Mmona nfong no bo ko agul lim go Betel a Dan 
\p  
\v 25 Owo Jeroboam kehm lange ekahme sennge Sekem go ejahbe ewong ji Efriim, fere lene o. Owo á mehle no song si Peniyel. 
\p  
\v 26 Jeroboam kehm gboko ntir go ege eltim re, <<Li are eti etul bahke feere go ebangenahb ji Devid.  
\v 27 Ane baa lꞌtahm song lim ajomjom go etahk Jehova go Jeusalem, bo bahke kpe feere song kehme eltoono ntula abo, Rehoboam ntula Juda. Bo bahk-m wulu, fere feere goji ntula Rehoboam.>> 
\p  
\v 28 Ntul ko elle ni abatubelle ebe, kehm song to elokelom agul na ebbal. Kehm bungu tong ane re, <<kpˈriidi sehng ka-n re wahn jo je go Jeusalem song kak Esowo go. Anebe Isreel a wo li asowo enyahne, bo ji yehken no lohng go Ijib.  
\v 29 Elokelom ajehng á bumu go Betel, jehko á bum go Dan.  
\v 30 Fvfo ejum jia ebjol abiafem ka anebe Isreel; ane jo je song kak elokelom ajehng ji jolo go Betel, fere tahm je fee song kak elokelom jehko go Dan.  
\v 31 Jeroboam si ntahk eblom go ero awong, fere tob yehke abalimajom go ellong ajoobo ane, jol afi bo jolem ane ba lohng etˈtohngo ji Levi.  
\v 32 Á bumu elkak go nfung elku, go nnyahng enehkeni, ana elkak nyi nkpatahk nyi bo limi go Juda, fere lim ajomjom go egudu njom. Á limi ana go Betel, lim ajom ka alokelom nya á ma lim. Fvfo go Betel, á tob yehke abalimajom kunu go adi ajom alimi nya á limi no.  
\v 33 Go nfung elku go nnyahng enehkeni, efung bio bi á yehke no antahng, á jo limi ajomjom go egudu njom ji á limi no go Betel. Ano wo á jo bum elkak nio ka anebe Isreel, fere jo song wahr egudu jo lim ajom. 
\c 13  
\s1 Nnyehnamahr Esowo bungu ebi abada njom nyi Jreroboam limi no 
\p  
\v 1 Nne Esowo kehm lohngo go Juda ba rehng ga Betel a ellum ni Jehova, ana Jeroboam yim go nkpe egudu njom re á lim njom.  
\v 2 Á kehm rabe wahre wahre go esamahr egudu njom re: Egudu njom, egudu njom! Ejum ji a ji Jehova ma bung re, <Bo bahke jele mmon go ebangenahb ji Devid, bo bahk-e gungu mbing re Josiya. Á bahke koko abalimajom ba awahre wahre adi, lim njom kunu o, bo ji kpi ajomjom lim a. Bo bahke fehke akahb ane kun-a o.>>>  
\v 3 Efung bꞌnehm o, nnyehnamahr Esowo tibi elliingi: <<A wo li elliingi ni Jehova ma tib: Egudu njom bahke wake, atong ma kun o bahke faade.>>  
\v 4 Ngare nyi ntula Jeroboam wuku ana nnenlum Esowo noo rabe ebi bade egudu njom go Betel, á kehm tanne ebo ebe eji á yim go egudu njom, kehm bungu re, <<Jabben ye!>> Wo ebo bi á tanne no ton nne Esowo noo sa wuumu, á kpeem ma feere ebo bio go ndi.  
\v 5 Fvfo, egudu njom bahnge, atong eme faade go ndi ana elliingi ni nne Esowo noo tibi no, sehng go ellum ni Jehova. 
\p  
\v 6 Owo ntul kehm bungu tong nne Esowo re, <<Gboongo Jehova Esowo eba, wo fere kak ero ka-m re ebo ebame fere jol ana wuku wuku.>> Ano wo nnenlum Esowo kehm gboongo Jehova, fvfo ebo ntul kehm feere jol ana wuku wuku. 
\p  
\v 7 Ntul kehm bungu tong nne Esowo re, <<Toon-m ba go etahk, wo ba li ejum alehke, fvfo m bahk-a yare ka ejum.>> 
\p  
\v 8 Wo nne Esowo faange ntul re, <<Jol afi a yange nsol kpee nyi a kpi no, fere ka-m ejang ajehng, n nehm ma feere toon-a, jol n nehm li ejum alehke, afi wo alahb edi jia.  
\v 9 Tibre elkahn lohng go ellum ni Jehova ba kpir-m re, <á lˈkehme elkehnge, ka tiki li nsol alehke afi wo alahb, jol ka feere toono mbang nyi á lohngo no ba.>>>  
\v 10 Ano wo, á toono mbang nyindiki, fvfo á kpeem toono mbang nyi á sehnge no ba go Betel. 
\p  
\v 11 Nkꞌkulu nnyehnamahr awohng lene o Betel. Abon ebe feere ba tong-e nsol kpee nyi nnyehnamahr Esowo ma lim efung bio. Bo tob tongo nde ebo nsol nyi á ma bungu tong ntul.  
\v 12 Ndea ebo kehm bahbe bo re, <<Mbang anyii á sennge no tahm?>> Owo abon ebe kehm-e tibi mbang nyi nnyehnamahr Esowo no lohng go Juda sennge no tahm.  
\v 13 Ano wo á kehm tongo abon re, <<Tooben mbvankang bum-m.>> Fvfo eji bo ma toobo mbvankang bum-e, á kehm wahre kuumu,  
\v 14 kehm kehme elfingi asongo jo toono mbang nyi nnyehnamahr Esowo sehnge no asongo. Á song kpiri nnyehnamahr Esowo noo jehk go nnahb eti nyi bo kpo lung re oak, kehm bahbe re, 
\p <<Wo wo li nnyehnamahr Esowo no lohng go Juda baa? 
\p Á kehm-e faange re, <<Me wo.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Owo nnyehnamahr kehm-e tongo re, <<Feere toonem wo ba li nsol egame etahk. 
\p  
\v 16 Nnyehnamahr Esowo kehm bungu re, <<N nehm ma feere, toon-a ba ega etahk, jol ejum alehke n nehm li afi alahb ma n nehm wo a na edi jia.  
\v 17 Elkahn lohng goji Jehova ba kpir-m re, <Ka tiki li ejum alehke o, afi wo alahb o, jol ka feere mbang nyi á lohngo no ba.> >> 
\p  
\v 18 Nkꞌkula nnyehnamahr kehm faange re, <<Me fvfo, me nnyehnamahr wo ana wo. Enjel bungu aname go ellum ni Jehova re: <Feere a ne song go ega etahk, eji á bahke ba li ejum alehke, fere wo alahb.> <Wo na ga á jo kim-e efahnge.>  
\v 19 Ano wo nnyehnamahr Esowo feere toon-e ba li nsol alehke fere wo alahb go ege etahk.  
\v 20 Ana bo jehk go ekpukuru, ellum ni Jehova kehm bake goji nkꞌkula nnyehnamahr, no me-e ko feere a ne.  
\v 21 Á kehm rabe tong nnyehnamahr Esowo no lohng go Juda ba re, <<Ji ji a ji Jehova ma bung re: <Wobten ellum ni Jehova, fvfo á bumem elkahn ni Jehova Esowo eba ka-a no.  
\v 22 Á feere ba, wob li nsol alehke fere wo alahb edi ji Jehova tong-a re wo kꞌli nsol, afi kꞌwo alahb. Eji li ano ngubjing enya bo nehm kpa kak go elahm bi babnso.> >>  
\v 23 Ngare nyi nnyehnamahr Esowo ma li nsol mal, fere wo alahb, nnyehnamahr no feere a ne ba, kehm ba toobo mbvankang enye bum-e.  
\v 24 Ana á jo jen asongo go mbang, egabe kehm ba kpir-e go mbang wul-e, ngubjing enye sa noongo go nlum mbang, mbvankang a egabe yiimi kohlo ekv eje.  
\v 25 Egom ane ba jo sehng mbang nyehne ngubjing nong go mbang, fere nyehn egabe yim kohlo ngubjing enye, wo bo tahme song rehng go mfam ejahbe nyi nkˈkulu nnyehnamahr noo lene no song tiingi. 
\p  
\v 26 Eji nnyehnamahr Esowo no ko-e no feere a ne, ngare nyi á jo feere kehnge wuku no, á bungu re, <<nlokeltum Esowo wo, no tene ellum ni lohng go nnyo mi Jehova. Jehova me-e faake ka egabe, ji me-e bob wul go mbang, jang jang ana ellum ni Jehova me-e kak erehke.>>  
\v 27 Nnyehnamahr kehm bungu tong abon ebe re, <<Toob-n mbvankang bum-m,>> bo kehm limi ano.  
\v 28 Owo á kehm lohngo tahm song nyehn ngubjing nong go mbang, go mbvankang a egabe yim kohl-e. Jol egabe ka jaake ngubjing, afi wul mbvankang.  
\v 29 Ano wo nnyehnamahr Esowo rodo ngubjing nyio nyi nlokeltum Esowo, kunu go njahma mbvankang, feere a nyi atahng nfam enye, re á ba ling-e, fere kpa-e kak.  
\v 30 Owo á kehm rodo ngubjing nyio song kpa kak go ege elahm, kehm noongo elkv ene, kehm bungu re, <<Eyee Mmonannee ewame!>>  
\v 31 Eji á m-e kpa kak, á kehm bungu tong abon ebe re, <<Me n lꞌkpo, kpa-m wahn kak go elahm bi bo kake nlokeltum Esowo noa. Roden akahb enyame bum kohlo nya nye.  
\v 32 Tib go etib bi á bungu no sehng go alum nya Jehova bade egudu njom ji li go Betel, fvfo bade ntahk eblom nya kun awahre wahre adi go ejahbe Samaria, bahke lohko jol go etingitingi. 
\p  
\v 33 Jol eji nsol nyia ma sehng, Jeroboam tikem yaange ebi abang enye, wo á kpe yehke na abalimajom ba ntahk eblom go ellong ajoobo ane. Nne awohng awohng no jo seb re á jol nlimanjom, á rod-e fuulu kunu go ntahk elom.  
\v 34 A wo jolo abiafem nya ebangenahb ji Jeroboam ji wahnge no ka bo gbo no, fere rannge go esamahr njini kpee. 
\c 14  
\s1 Enyehnamahr Ji Ahija Nyehne Bada Jeroboam 
\p  
\v 1 Ngare nyio Abija mmona Jeroboam gboo eyam,  
\v 2 owo Jeroboam kehm bungu tong nkal re, <<Song, wo song yaange nsol ebjing bo ki-a liingi re wo nkala Jeroboam wo. Wo song go Silo. Ahija ji nnyehnamahr li o, ye ji tong-m re, m bahke jolo ntul no ane baa.  
\v 3 Rod ngbu ebred na ewubu wo fili, a akare, go ekpuma akehng ekon, wo song go ege. Á bahk-a tongo ji bahke limi mmon noa.>>  
\v 4 Ano wo nkala Jeroboam kehm limi ji á bungu no, fere mehl tahm etahk Ahija go Silo. 
\p Ngare nyia Ahija nehme kpe nyehn, tib yebkul.  
\v 5 Wo Jehova ebtong Ahija re, <<Nkala Jeroboam kpꞌbake re á ba bahb-a bada mmon ewe, tib mmon kpꞌyame, fvfo nfaange nyi a nyi a bahk-e faange. Ngare nyi á ma ba, á bahke limi awini re ye nnenkal nondikandiki wo.>>  
\v 6 Wo eji Ahija wuku akpade eljen ene go mbutahk, á kehm bungu re, <<Ba yel, nkal no Jeroboam. Awini nyaa lohngo renan? Bo ma-m tum tv-a, a ebi etib.  
\v 7 Song, tong Jeroboam re, ejum ji a ji Jehova Esowo bi Isreel bungu no re: <M mehl-a wahre go ellong ane, fere lim-a nfilane go ellong anebe Isreel, ane ebame.  
\v 8 N yange eti etul, yehke go ebangenahb ji Devid, fere feere a ji ka-a, wo jol, a ka jol ana Devid nlokeltum ewame, ye ji bumu atahm enyame, fere toon-m a eltim eltim ene kpee, á jo limi nsol nyi jo nob go egame esamahr.  
\v 9 Woblim abꞌbi sehnge ane ba gbo mbang jini ka wo. Woblim asowo nyako ka elna, alokelom nya bo ko akuungu lim, á ma-m lim me n rak atahng, a ma-m sennge njahm. 
\p  
\v 10 <<<Tib go esi jia, m bahke koko elrannge ba go ebangenahb ji Jeroboam. M bahke wulu nnenlum awohng awohng go ebangenahb ji Jeroboam go Isreel, jolo nju, afi nne no ma for. M bahke jahme etahk ji Jeroboam ana nne kpo jahm ebimbim, tete fi kpee.  
\v 11 Nne awohng awohng no li ka Jeroboam no kpoo go atahng nfam ebv bahk-e lehke, wo bo ji kpoo go ekulugbe, nruk nyi bahke lehke bo. Me Jehova wo ma bung!> 
\p  
\v 12 Go ega, feere song kehnge. Ngare nyi a lꞌsi yꞌyel go ega nfam, mmon noo bahke kpoko.  
\v 13 Anebe Isreel kpee bahke noongo elkv ene, fere kpa-e kak. Ye ntahng ntahng wo li nne no li ka Jeroboam no bo bahk-e kpake kak, tibre ye ntahng ntahng wo li go ebangenahb ji Jeroboam, ye ji Jehova Esowo bi Isreel ma nyehn ejum ji ma lim Jehova ma bel eyebatahng. 
\p  
\v 14 <<Jehova bahke yehke ntul ka elne antahng no bahke fili Isreel, no bahke tane ebangenahb ji Jeroboam. Jol anv, ebbom ellimi.\f + \fr 14:14 \ft Alum nyaa go ntoora anyo mi Hibru lenngem\f* 
\v 15 Fvfo Jehova bahke kake Isreel erem, eji bahke jolo ana elnyane ni kpꞌfuungu go alahb. Jehova bahke yehke Isreel go nnooba ndi nyi á ka babnde ebo, fere kam bo faade rehng go Aya ma Yufrat, tibre boblim Jehova ebbel erakatahng, eji bo ma lim ago nya esowo bi Asera.  
\v 16 Fvfo Jehova bahke yake Isreel abo, tib go esi abiafem nya Jeroboam ma lim, nya á ma lim anebe Isreel ma tob song lim.>> 
\p  
\v 17 Owo nkala Jeroboam kehm mehle o tahm, fere ba rehng go Tirja. Ana á ba siiri akpade go eti mbu, mmon noo soro kpo.  
\v 18 Bo kpa-e kak, Isreel kpee noongo elkv ene, ana Jehova bungu no sehng go nnyo mi nlokeltum ewe, nnyehnamahra Ahija. 
\p  
\v 19 Nsol nyehko nyi jolo go ngare nyi ntula Jeroboam jo fili edi, nta nyi á jo nok fvfo ana á jo fili edi, bo nyono go awer aka nya atul bao ba anebe Isreel.  
\v 20 Á fili edi eltahl a nnya ebal, kehm kpoko. Fvfo Nadab mmon ewe wo ko nji etul enye. 
\s1 Rehoboam ba jolo Ntula Juda 
\p  
\v 21 Rehoboam mmona Solomon jolo ntul go Juda. Ngare nyi bo bob-e etul yebkang nnya atahl abal a elya anehng, á fili ejahbe elku a nnya ebal go Jeusalem, egburu nfam ejahbe nyi Jehova yehke no kpee go atꞌtohngo nya Isreel, nyi á bahke kake mbing enye. Nnyehn bo jo lung-e re Naama; á lohng go Amon. 
\p  
\v 22 Ngare nyi Rehoboam jo fili edi anebe Isreel limi abꞌbi. Abiafem ebo nyao melle egburu erakatahng ji Jehova sehnge ana nya babnde ebo limi no.  
\v 23 Bo si ntahk eblom bum elbo, atal njom, bo jamme ago nya bo jo kak asowo anebkal nya bo kpo lung re asera, go nwahre wahre ewong anyehng anyehng, a ala nti nya ma nyange.  
\v 24 Fvfo aneblum ba jo jen asꞌsa go ntahk eblom jolo go ejahbe, bo rodo elbo kak go abi nsol nya ajahbe nyako jo lim, bo ji Jehova ma kam bo go esamahr bi anebe Isreel. 
\p  
\v 25 Eji ntula Rehoboam ma fili ejahbe nnya elon, Sisak ntula Ijib kehm ba nok a Jeusalem.  
\v 26 Á ba yehke nsol kpee go etahk Jehova, a nsol nyi woomo go ekpasiki. Á rodo ejum ajehng ajehng, fere buda akum agul kpee nya Solomon limi no.  
\v 27 Owo ntula Rehoboam ko abilikpi lim akum go enyo jio ji akum agul, fere rod ka atubesi ababˈbaabe adi, ba jolo go eltum go mbuga mi ekpasiki ntul.  
\v 28 Ngare anyehng anyehng nyi ntul lꞌje go etahk ji Jehova, ababꞌbaabe jo fili akum nyao, fere feere a nya song bum ekpꞌkpa nsol abumu bo lꞌlim mal. 
\p  
\v 29 Bade nsol nyehko nyi jolo ngare nyi Rehoboam jo fili edi, a nsol kpee nyi á limi no, bo nyono go awer nya aka nya atul ba Isreel.  
\v 30 Rehoboam a Jeroboam jolo go ebta ngare kpe kpe.  
\v 31 Owo Rehoboam kehm kpoko, bo song kpa-e kak go eyele ebo go ejahbe ji Devid. Nyehn bo jo lung re Naama á lohng go Amon. Fvfo Abija mmon ewe, wo ji nji etul enye. 
\c 15  
\s1 Abija Ntula Juda 
\p  
\v 1 Elku a nnya era nyi Jeroboam mmona Nebati kpi Isreel fili, owo Abija ba jol ntul no Juda,  
\v 2 á kuumu go Jeusalem jo fili ejahbe nnya era. Nnyehn bo jo lung-e re Maaka mmona Abisalom.  
\v 3 Á limi elkohn abiafem anyehng anyehng kpee nya nde no tohko jol ka ye limi no, nya jolo go ege esamahr; eltim ene á yakem kpee ka Jehova Esowo ebe ana nde no nkul Devid limi no.  
\v 4 Eji jolo jol ano, wo go esi ji Devid, Jehova Esowo ebe ka-e ka ellennge go Jeusalem, eji á ka-e mmon no bahke jehke etul toon-e, fere lim Jeusalem bel atahne.  
\v 5 Jehova limi ejum jia tibre, Devid limi ejum ji jolo go nseenge go esamahr Jehova, fvfo á kanem elbumu elkahn anehng anehng ngare nyi á jolo go elkpin, sehngem ji á limi no bade Yuraya nnea Hiti. 
\p  
\v 6 Ebta bi gbo Rehoboam abola Jeroboam soro asi ano ano ngare nyi Abija jolo go elkpin.  
\v 7 Bade nsol nyehko nyi jolo ngare nyi Abija jo fili edi, a nsol kpee nyi á limi no, bo nyon go nwer aka nya atul ba Juda. Abija aboloa Jeroboam jolo go ebta.  
\v 8 Abija kpo, bo kpa-e kak go eyele babnde, go ejahbe ji Devid. Asa mmon ewe wo ko nji etul enye. 
\s1 Asa Jolo Ntul No Juda 
\p  
\v 9 Ngare nyi Jeroboam ma fili Isreel nnya eltahl, owo Asa kuumu etul go Juda.  
\v 10 fvfo á kuumu go Jeusalem nnya atahl abal a elya anehng. Nnyehn no nkul bo jo lung-e re Maaka mmon no Abisalom.  
\v 11 Asa limi nsol nyi jolo go nseenge go esamahr Jehova, ana nde Devid limi no.  
\v 12 Á kame aneblum ba jo lim asꞌsa go ntahk eblom, fere rannge alokelom kpee nya babnde ma lim.  
\v 13 Á tob kame nnyehn no nkul Maaka yehke bum go nkpe ana nnyehn no ntul, tibre á bele ebi elokelom ji á limi re bo jo ko kak Asera. Wo Asa kimi elokelom tub go, fere rod song jahm fi go edamme ji Kidron.  
\v 14 Jol eji á ki rˈrannge ntahk eblom kpee, eltim ni Asa á rodo kpe kpe ka Jehova ngare kpee nyi á jolo go elkpin.  
\v 15 Á ko asilva a agul a ajoobo nsol nyehko nya ye a nde ma rod kak Jehova go ebo, ba a nya go etahk Esowo ji Jehova. 
\p  
\v 16 Asa ntula Juda a Baasa ntula Isreel jolo go ebta ngare kpe kpe, eji bo jo fili adi.  
\v 17 Baasa ntula Isreel kehm mehle ebta a anebe Juda, á song lange ekahme elbaabe sennge ejahbe Rama kak, eji nne awohng awohng lꞌkꞌlohng, afi sehng yel go edi ndi ji Asa ntula Juda.  
\v 18 Owo Asa kehm rodo asilva a agul kpee nya sa go adi elkuuru nya etahk ji Jehova, a ekpasiki eje. Á faake kak atubesi abalimeltum ebe, kehm tumu bo tv goji Ben-Hadad mmon no Tabrimon, mmon no Hejion, ntul no Aram, ye ji jo fili edi go Damaskosi.  
\v 19 Á kehm bahbe bo re, bo tong ntul Aram re,<<Nong wahr ko nwongo, wo, a me, ana nsoo no ewame ko nwongo a nso no ewa. Nyehne, nsol asilva a agul ga nya m ma tum tv-a ana ayare. Anv, yake nwongo anyehng anyehng nyi a ma ko a Baasa ntula Isreel, eji á lꞌyak-m abo.>>  
\v 20 Ntula Ben Hadad taame ji ntula Asa bungu no, kehm tumu atubesi nsoja enye tv go ajahbe Isreel. Á noko ga ajahbe Ijon, Dan, Abel Beti Maaka, a Kenereti go erohko ji Naftali.  
\v 21 Eji Baasa wuku jia, á rahke eltuungu Rama, fere feere go Tirija.  
\v 22 Owo ntula Asa kehm kake elkahn ka Juda kpee, nne awohng awohng limm no ki woomo go atahng, bo song sol atal go Rama, a akpidi nti nya Baasa jo ko lim eltum. Nya nya ntula Asa ko si Geba ji li go Benjamin, tob ko si Mijipa.  
\v 23 Bade nsol nyehko kpee, nyi jolo ngare nyi Asa jo fili edi, a nsol kpee nyi á male lim, kpee nsol nyi á limi no, a ajahbe nya á si no, bo nyono kpee go nwer aka nya atul ba Juda. Eji á ma kul á gbo eyam akpade.  
\v 24 Owo Asa kehm kpoko, bo kpa-e kak, eyele ji ejahbe nde Devid. Jehosafad mmon ewe wo ko nji etul enye. 
\s1 Nadab jolo ntula Isreel 
\p  
\v 25 Nadab mmona Jeroboam ba kuumu etul go Isreel go etoono elya ni Asa kpi Juda fili, á fili Isreel nnya ebal.  
\v 26 Á limi abi nsol go asamahr bi Jehova, á jo jene go abang nya nde jo jen, fere jo lim abiafem nyanehm nya nde limi anebe Isreel re bo jo lim.  
\v 27 Baasa mmona Ahija ji lohng go ebangenahb ji Isaka lame kak-e, fere wul-e go Gibeton ejahbe Filita, ngare nyi Nadab a anebe Isreel kpee ma sennge ejahbe kak.  
\v 28 Baasa wulu Nadab eji ma kang nnya era nyi Asa kuumu etul go Juda, fere ko nji etul enye go Isreel. 
\p  
\v 29 Ana Baasa bomo edi afili, á wulu ebangenahb ji Jeroboam kpee. Jol á yakem nne awohng awohng no sa go elkpin, á rannge bo kpee, jang jang ana Jehova bungu sehng go nnyo mi nlokeltum ewe Ahija ji lohng go Silo-  
\v 30 Jia limi tib go abiafem nya Jeroboam limi no, fere Isreel bo lim abiafem, fvfo á tob limi Jehova Esowo bi Isreel rak atahng. 
\p  
\v 31 Bade nsol nyehko nyi jolo ngare nyi Nadab jo fili edi, a nsol kpee nyi á limi no, bo nyono go nwer aka nya atul ba Isreel.  
\v 32 Asa ntula Juda a Baasa ntula Isreel jolo go ebta ngare kpee nyi bo jo fili adi ebo. 
\s1 Baasa jolo ntula Isreel 
\p  
\v 33 Eji ma kang nnya era nyi Asa ntula Juda kuumu etul, Baasa mmona Ahija ba kuumu etul ka Isreel kpee go Tija, fvfo á fili Isreel eltahl a nnya eni.  
\v 34 Á limi abꞌbi go esamahr bi Jehova, á jo jene go abang nya Jeroboam, fere jo lim abiafem nyanehm nya nde limi anebe Isreel re bo jo lim. 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong nnyehnamahra Jehu mmona Hanani, fere bade Baasa re,  
\v 2 <<N rod-a ana nne no ane ki-a nyi re wo ba jol nfiladi, fili Isreel ane ebame, wo á fere jo jen go abang nya Jeroboam, fere lim ane ebame jo lim abꞌbi, fere jo lim-m m bel erakatahng go esi abiafem ebo nyao.  
\v 3 Wo, Baasa a nlaaga enya kpee, m bahke limi nlaaga enya ana nyi Jeroboam mmona Nebati.  
\v 4 Nne awohng awohng no li ka Baasa no kpoo go nfam ebv bahk-e lehke, wo bo ji kpoo go ekulugbe nruk nyi bahke lehke bo.>> 
\p  
\v 5 Bade nsol nyehko nyi jolo no ngare nyi Baasa jo fili edi, nya á limi no fere bel, bo nyono go nwer aka nya atul ba Isreel.  
\v 6 Owo Baasa kehm kpoko bo kpa-e go eyele babnde, go Tirija. Ela mmon ewe ko nji etul enye.  
\v 7 Wo fvfo, ellum ni Jehova kehm bungu sehng goji nnyehnamahra Jehu ji mmona Hanani, bade Baasa a ebangenahb eje, tib go abꞌbi nya á ma lim go esamahr bi Jehova, lim Jehova bel erakatahng go nsol nyi á limi no, fere jol ana ebangenahb Jeroboam, fvfo tibre Baasa rannge ebangenahb ji Jeroboam 
\s1 Ela ntul no Isreel 
\p  
\v 8 Go eltahl a nnya erakera nyi ntula Asa jo fili Juda, Ela mmona Baasa ba kuumu etul go Isreel, fvfo á fili nfam go Tirija nnya ebal. 
\p  
\v 9 Wo Jimri, ntubesi nsoja ewe awohng, ye ji jo fili ejang amvtv akuungu enye, lame kak-e. Ela jolo go Tirija ngare nyio, á woo jo bˈbuumu go etahk ji Aja, ntubesi no ababˈbaabe ekpasiki go Tirija.  
\v 10 Jimri kehm bake ba yel, ba rum-e tub, fere wul-e, ngare nyio ebkang eltahl a nnya esehma nyi ntula Asa kpi Juda fili. Owo á fere ko nji etul enye.  
\v 11 Ngare nyꞌnehm o nyi Jimri bomo edi afili, á ma ji go nji etul, á kehm wulu ebangenahb Baasa kpee. Nnenlum awohng awohng bo we yakem, afi fere jolo ekunu, afi ntem.  
\v 12 Ano wo Jimri rannge ebangenahb ji Baasa kpee, ana ellum ni Jehova bungu no bada Baasa sehng go nnyo mi Jehu nnyehnamahr-  
\v 13 tib go abiafem kpee nya Baasa a mmon ewe Ela ma lim, a nya bo ma lim Isreel bo ma lim, boblim Jehova Esowo bi Isreel ebbel erakatahng go alokelom ebo nya ki lohng ejumjum. 
\p  
\v 14 Bade nsol nyehko nyi jolo no ngare nyi Ela jo fili edi, a nsol kpee nyi á limi no, bo nyono go nwer aka nya atul ba Isreel. 
\s1 Jimri jolo ntula Isreel 
\p  
\v 15 Jimri bomo Isreel elfili go Tirija go eltahl a nnya esehma nyi ntula Asa jo fili Juda, wo Jimri fili ejahbe nfung na esehma nyi nyi. Nsoja nyi Isreel bele edi erekekv kohlo Gibeton ejahbe anebe Filista  
\v 16 Eji nsoja nyi anebe Isreel ba jolo go edi erekekv wuku re Jimri ebtoobo ebi bada ntul, fere wul-e, bo yehke Omri, ji ntubesi nsoja, á jol ntul no Isreel efung bꞌnehm o go edi erekekv.  
\v 17 Owo Omri a Isreel kpee kehm mehle go Gibeton, song noongo sennge Tirija kak.  
\v 18 Ana Jimri nyehne re bob nok ko ejahbe, á kehm beke song yel etahntahn ekpˈkpa ji ekpasiki, fere kak agun sennge elne kak. Ano wo á kpo no,  
\v 19 tib go abiafem nya á ma lim, jo lim abꞌbi go esamahr bi Jehova, fere jo jen go abang nya Jeroboam a abiafem nyanehm nya Jeroboam limi anebe Isreel re bo jo lim. 
\p  
\v 20 Bada nsol nyehko nyi jolo no ngare nyi Jimri jo fili edi, a ntoobo ewul nyi á bele no, bo nyono go nwer aka nya atul ba Isreel. 
\s1 Omri jolo ntula Isreel 
\p  
\v 21 Wo anebe Isreel kehm yabe ejang ebbal; ejang behko jolo ka Tibni mmona Ginati re á jol ntul, ejang ane jehko jolo ka Omri.  
\v 22 Wo ane ba jo toono Omri tahne go ebta sehnge ane ba jo toono Tibni mmona Ginati. Bo wulu Tibni, Omri fere jol ntul. 
\p  
\v 23 Go eltahl a nnya ewubu a elya anehng nyi Asa jolo ntul no Juda, owo Omri kuumu etul ka Isreel, á fili edi ewuba nnya ebal. Go ewuba ebal nyio á jolo go Tirija fili edi nnya erakera.  
\v 24 Á gunu ewong ji Samaria go ebo nnenlum no bo jo lung-e re Sema go ebahk asilva akpohko atahltahl nkpel ewubu a nkpel eni, fere si ejahbe kunu o, jo lung re Samaria, á gungu mbing nyio kpiidi a Sema ye ji tohko jol nfono ewong jio wuku wuku. 
\p  
\v 25 Wo Omri limi abiafem go esamahr bi Jehova, fere gbal sehnge ane ba gbo mbang kuumu etul ka-e.  
\v 26 Á jo jene go abang kpee nya Jeroboam mmona Nebati, jo lim abiafem nyanehm, nya Jeroboam limi anebe Isreel jo lim, jo lim Jehova Esowo bi Isreel bel erakatahng go esi alokelom ebo nya ki lohng ejumjum.  
\v 27 Bade nsol nyehko nyi jolo no ngare nyi Omri jo fili edi, a nsol nyi á limi no, go nta nyi á noko no, bo nyono go nwer aka nya atul ba Isreel.  
\v 28 Omri kpo, bo kpa-e kak go Samaria. Fvfo mmon ewe Ehab wo ko nji etul enye. 
\s1 Ehab Ntula Isreel 
\p  
\v 29 Go eltahl a nnya elku a nnya era nyi Asa jolo ntula Juda, Ehab mmona Omri ba kuumu etul go Isreel, á fili Isreel go Samaria go eltahl a nnya ebal.  
\v 30 Ehab mmona Omri limi abꞌbi go esamahr bi Jehova sehnge ane kpee ba ma tohko jol atul ka ye.  
\v 31 Jol-e nehka nehka re á jo jen go mbang abiafem nyi Jeroboa mmona Nebati, wo á fere ko Jejibel mmon no nkal go elbal no ntula Etibaal ji anebe Sidon, fere jo loko Baal, fere jo kak-e.  
\v 32 Á limi egudu njom ji Baal go etahk elom Baal ji á si go Samaria.  
\v 33 Ehab tob lo ego ji Asera, fere lim nsol gbalee nyi jo ka Jehova Esowo bi Isreel erakatahng, sehnge nya atul kpee ba ma tohko jol ka-e.  
\v 34 Go ngare nyi Ahab, Hiel ji nnea Betel, ye wo tuungu Jeriko si. Wo eji Hiel jo bum nnahb ekahme nyi nfam nyio, ngbokambanga mmon ewe no nlum Abiram wo kpo. Fvfo ana á jo lim ati mbu re mal nkahla mmon ewe no nlum Segub, tob kpo, jang jang ana alum nya Jehova bungu sehng go nnyo mi Josua mmon no Nun. 
\c 17  
\s1 Ana Ekumgbakela Le Elayija 
\p  
\v 1 Elayija nnea Tisibe ji li go Giled, kehm tongo Ehab re, <<Ana Jehova Esowo bi Isreel bi li go elkpin, ye ji n kp-e loko, ebohng abehng abehng nehm kpe na, jol elahb nehm kpe na, go abon nnya ba kpˈbake, no me wo bungu re na.>> 
\p  
\v 2 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Elayija re,  
\v 3 <<Mehl edi jia, wo song go ero nfam, song biiri go kohlo ebgba Kereti go ero aya Jodan  
\v 4 A bahke jo wo alahb go ebgba, wo fere jo li ji akumgbakela bahke koko ba ka-a, tibre me n ka bo nsahm re bo jo ko nsol alehke ba ka-a.>> 
\p  
\v 5 Ano wo Elayija mehle song lim ji Jehova me-e tong. Á tahme go ebgba bi bo kpo lung re Keriti, ero aya Jodan song jol o.  
\v 6 Akumgbakela jo ko ebred a nnyam ba ka-e efungfu, ngare elgung bo tob ko ebred a nnyam ba ka-e, á fere jo wo alahb go ebgba. 
\s1 Nkalebun No Jolo Go Jarefati 
\p  
\v 7 Eji ma kang abon afung, ebgba bio kehm kake, tibre elahb joom kpe na go ndi nyio.  
\v 8 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Elayija re:  
\v 9 <<Mehl song elwaare go Jarefati go erohko ji Sidon, wo song jol o. Me n toobo nkalebun o edi jio re, á jo ka-a nsol alehke.>>  
\v 10 Ano wo á kehm tahme go Jarefati. Eji á rehnge go eti mbu ji ejahbe jio, nkalebun jolo o jo rak nkun. Á kehm-e lungu kehme bahbe re, <<A bahk-m ma ka abon alahb go ega ekpꞌkpuk me n woa?>>  
\v 11 Ana á tahme alahb lim ba ka-e, á kehm kpe bung a ne re, <<Titi, ko mmobahk ebred ba kam.>> 
\p  
\v 12 Wo nnenkal noo kehm-e faange re, << Etingitingi ana Jehova Esowo eba li go elkpin, >>Ejum alehke ajehng ajehng n kpimm, sehngem abon abe ana ntiil ba wob go mmotu a abon akehng go ekpuma. N kpi abon nkun rak tahm aba go etahk, song lam nsol nyi me a mmon ewame e lˈli mal, e bahke jehke kpo njal.>>  
\v 13 Elayija kehm-e tongo re, <<Ka fahl. Song etahk, wo lim ana a bungu no. Wo, gbo mbang lim mmobahk ebred ntiil ba kam go abe nya a kpi no, wo kehm song lim nya wo a mmon ewa.  
\v 14 Ejum ji a ji Jehova Esowo bi Isreel ma bung re: <Etu abe nehm tiki mal, jol ekpuma akehng nehm tiki tob mal, tete efung bio bi Jehova bahke nake elahb go ndi.>>> 
\p  
\v 15 Nkalebun noo kehm tahme, song lim ana Elayija tong-e no. Ano wo nsol lehke jolo ka Elayija efung abehng abehng, a nkalebun noo a ebangenahb eje.  
\v 16 Etu abe tikem mal, jol ekpuma akehng tikem tob mal, jang jang ana ellum ni Jehova bungu no sehng go nnyo mi Elayija.  
\v 17 Eji ma kang abon afung, mmona nnenkal no kpi etahk kehm ba gbo eyam. Mmon noo, eyam kehm ba riidi na riidi, esˈkohro á kpo.  
\v 18 Nnenkal noo kehm tongo Elayija re, <<Nne Esowo, jenjii a ma-m lim ana? A ba na re wo ba gbib-m nnahba go egame abiafema, fere wul mmon ewama?>>  
\v 19 Elayija kehm tongo nnenkal noo re, <<Ka-m mmon ewa.>> Elayija kehm koko mmon noo go ege ebo, kehm-e rodo tahm a ne go ero enyong, edi ji á jolo no, song kun-e go ege edilnong.  
\v 20 Owo á kehm rabe lung Jehova re, <<Jehova Esowo ebame, wob ko elkohn ebi ejum ana jia ba kunu nkalebun noa no n lene a nea, eji a ma limm mmon ewe ma kpo?  
\v 21 Owo á kehm tanne bulu mmon noa nkpel era, kehm rabe lung Jehova go ero akake re, <<Jehova Esowo ebame, feere elkpin mmon noa ba ka-e!>> 
\p  
\v 22 Jehova kehm wuku ero bi Elayija kake no, feere elkpin mmon kak-e, á fere jol go elkpin.  
\v 23 Elayija kehm rodo mmon, fere badde a ne ba ga ekpꞌkpa nnahbandi. Á rod-e faake ka nnyehn, kehm bungu re, <<Nyehne, mmon ewa, noa elkpin!>>  
\v 24 Owo Nnenkal noo kehm tongo Elayija re, <<Anv me n kahn re, wo lohko li Nne Esowo, fere nyehn re ellum ni Jehova go ega nnyo lohko li etingitingi.>> 
\c 18  
\s1 Elayija abola Obadiya 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ekidi ma lab, go nnya era nyi elahb kala kpe na, Jehova kehm tongo Elayija re, <<Song, wo song tib elna go esamahr bi Ehab, fvfo m bahke tumu elahb tv go ndi.>>  
\v 2 Ano wo Elayija tahme re á song tib elne go esamahr bi Ehab. 
\p Ngare nyia njal nyia gbalee go Samaria,  
\v 3 fvfo Ehab lungu Obadiya ji jolo nne no jo fili ekpasiki eje. (Obadiya jolo nne no yake elne ka Jehova fere jo kak-e.  
\v 4 Ana Jejibel jo wul abanyehnamahr ba Jehova, Obadiya\f + \fr 18:3 \ft Obadaya: Obadaya jia sang nyono nwer nyi li go nkˈkulu egbanngaung\f* ebrod abanyehnamahr bako ane atahl alon song behr go egong na ebbal, ane atahl abal ane awubu go egong ajehng ajehng, fere jo ka bo nsol alehke a alahb.)  
\v 5 Ahab tongo Obadiya re, <<Song yannge go adi kpee, a abing elahb go adamme. Fundiki e bahke ma nyehn abon ajele ba e bahke ma ko ba ka anyˈnya a ebvakang bo li kˈkpo, eji e lˈkˈwul nyam enyahre anyehng anyehng.>>  
\v 6 Ano wo bo bake elbo ndi nyio ana bo bahke yannge, Ahab je ejang bˈbe, fvfo Obadiya je ejang behko. 
\p  
\v 7 Ana Obadiya jo jen asongo, Elayija ba kpir-e. Obadiya lˈliingi Elayija, gong kok esi-e, fere bung re, <<Nsoo ewame Elayija, wo lohko yim aa?>> 
\p  
\v 8 Elayija kehm-e faange re, <<Ee me wo, song tong nso ewa re, Elayija li a.>>> 
\p  
\v 9 Obadiya kehm-e bahbe re, <<Ebi ajii m ma lim ji, a kpꞌsebe re wo faake me nlokeltum ewa ka Ehab á wul-e?  
\v 10 Etingitingi ana Jehova Esowo eba li go elkpin, ejahbe ajehng ajehng limm, afi ejahbe etul, ji nsoo ntul ewame kala tum nne re bo seb-a. Fvfo ejahbe, afi ejahbe etul ajehng ajehng lꞌbung re, go eji bo a limm, á bahke limi bo, bo tir re bo wa-a ka nyehn.  
\v 11 Wo anv, a kpꞌsebe re me n song tong nsoo ntul ewame re, <Elayija li a.>  
\v 12 N nehme kahn edi ji Etohko ji Jehova bahk-a rodo tahm, n lꞌtahm-a sa a. N lˈ tahm song tong Ehab, fvfo á tohk-a fere nyehn, á bahk-m wulu. Ga me nlokeltum ewa ebkak Jehova bomo ngare nyi n jolo njangkun.  
\v 13 Nsoo, a wuk-m ji n limi no, ngare nyi Jejibel jo wul abanyehnamahr ba Jehovaa? M behre abanyehnamahr ba Jehova, ane atahl alon go egong na ebbal, ane atahl abal ane awubu go egong ajehng ajehng, fere jo ka bo nsol alehke a alahb.  
\v 14 Wo anv, a kp-m tongo re, me n song tong nsoo ntul re, <Elayija li a.> Á bahk-m wulu!>> 
\p  
\v 15 Elayija kehm bungu re, <<Etingitingi ana Jehova ji Kpo fili elbung a ndi li go elkpin, ye ji n kp-e loko, etingitingi m bahke tiki ko elname song tib Ehab lela.>> 
\s1 Elayija Go Ewong Ji Kamel 
\p  
\v 16 Ano Obadiya mehle song kpiri Ehab kehm-e tongo, fvfo Ehab tahme song kpiri Elayija.  
\v 17 Eji Ehab nyehne Elayija, á kehm bungu tong-e re, <<Wo wo a, wo ji kpꞌkake Isreel agbiinga?>> 
\p  
\v 18 Elayija kehm faange re, <<N ka tiki seb ntong anyehng anyehng ka Isreel. Wo a ebangenahb nso, wahn ba ma ko ntong bo ka Isreel. Wahn ebten nkahn nyi Jehova, fere kpꞌtoono alokelom nya Baal.  
\v 19 Anv, ku anebe Isreel go nkpohko anyehng anyehng kpee, wahn ba kpir-m go Ewong ji Kamel. Wahn ko abanyehnamahr ba baal, ane atahltahl ane atahl abal ane awubu, a abanyehnamahr ba Asera ane atahltahl, bo ji kpo li nsol go ekpukuru ji Jejibel.>> 
\p  
\v 20 Ano wo Ehab kehm tumu ellum tv Isreel kpee, fere ko abanyehnamahr ba a bo go Egburu Ewong ji Kamel.  
\v 21 Elayija kehm tahme song yiimi go esamahr ane, kehm bungu re, << Bahke kange renan ń kehm gboko ntir bade eyake ebbal bia? Lꞌjol re Jehova Esowo bi, toonen ye, wo lꞌfere jol re Baal Esowo bi toonen ye. 
\p Wo nnene bungem ejumjum 
\p  
\v 22 Owo Elayija kehm bungu tong bo re, <<Me ntahng ntahng wo ma sa go ellong abanyehnamahr ba Jehova, wo Baal kpi abanyehnamahr ane atahltahl ane atahl abal ane awubu.  
\v 23 Song koon nlum efong na abal ba ka-r. Nong abannyehnamahr ba baal yehke anyehng ba-e, fere kiim-e kunu go nkun, bo kꞌkak agun. M bahke tob ba nluma nfong nyehko, fere tob kiimi kunu go nkun, jol agun n nehm kak.  
\v 24 Owo ḿ bahke lungu go mbing esowo ebahne, fvfo m bahke lungu go mbing nyi Jehova. Esowo bi lˈfaange go agun__ye wo li Esowo.>> 
\p Owo ane kpee kehm bungu re, <<Ji a ma bung ebnob.>> 
\p  
\v 25 Elayija kehm bungu tong abanyenamahr ba Baal re, <<Yehk-n nluma nfong awohng, wahn gbo mbang lim njom, tib ń li go egom. Lungen go mbing nyi esowo ebahne, wo agun nya ń lꞌkꞌkak.>>  
\v 26 Ano wo bo kehm rodo nluma nfong nyi bo ka bo, song wul. 
\p Owo bo kehm kehme elrabe jo lung mbing nyi Baal, bomo efungfu tete efin yiimi re, <<Baal, faang-r me!>> Wo nfaange jolem; nnene faangem. Fvfo bo jo bahne sennge egudu njom ji bo limi no. 
\p  
\v 27 Eji efin ma yiimi, Elayija kehm kehme bo nyok. Á kehm tongo bo re, <<Raben wꞌwahre! Etingitingi á lohko li esowo! Fundiki á kpˈtiri fee, afi á kpi eltum lim, tohko jol ano á li mbang eljen. Bahke ma jol re á nong go ellu, fvfo nobo re á nyahme.>>  
\v 28 Ano wo bo jo rabe wahre wahre, jo boomo elbo akahngkahng a nkong, ana eljini ebo jolo no, tete alung jo lohng fab.  
\v 29 Eji nnv ma ren, bo soro asi jo nyehn agbehre nngaane amahr ebo, tete ngare rehng nyi bo kpo lim njom nyi elgung. Wo nfaange jolem, nnene faangem, nnene jolem no wuungu atung. 
\p  
\v 30 Owo Elayija kehm tongo ane kpee re, <<Jeeren ba egame.>> Bo kehm bake ege, Elayija kehm tuungu egudu njom ji Jehova ji ma rannge.  
\v 31 Elayija rodo ewubu atal abal, eltal anehng jo jolo ka etꞌtohngo ajehng go atꞌtohngo nya lohng go elwo ni Jekob, ye ji Jehova bungu a ne rea, <<Mbing enya bo bahke jo lung-a re Isreel.>>  
\v 32 Á ko atal nyao lim egudu njom go mbing nyi Jehova, fere kpa ekpabingi sennge kak, ji bahke ma yel egalon alahb ebni.  
\v 33 Á kehm ba kono nkun, fere ba nfong nyio rod kunu go nkun. Owo á kehm tongo bo re, <<Tuken etu alahb na ebni bi nlen, wahn yaange wohngo go ejum njom nyio a nkun. Bo kehm limi ano. 
\p  
\v 34 Á bungu re, <<Kpeen lim ano, bo kpe lim ano. Á kpe tong bo re, <<Kpeen lim jol nkpel era,>> bo kpe lim ano nkpel era.  
\v 35 Alahb mao kehm kehme elfaabe go egudu njom, fere rur ekpabingi ji li sennge egudu njom jio. 
\p  
\v 36 Eji ngare nyi bo kpo lim njom ma rehng, owo Elayija nnyehnamahr kehm lohng ba yiimi kohlo egudu njom fere kak ero re, <<Jehova Esowo bi Ebraham, Aesik a Isreel, nong bo kahn lela re wo wo li Esowo go Isreel, fere kahn re me wo li nlokeltum ewa, fvfo n kpi nsol nyia lim kpee ana a ka-m elkahn.  
\v 37 Faang-m Jehova, Faang-m, eji ane baa lꞌkahn re wo Jehova, wo Esowo bi, fvfo re á kpi ntim ebo sennge feere go ega.  
\v 38 Owo agun kehm lohngo goji Jehova ba lul nsol njom, nkun, atal a ndi a ndi kpee, fere lahbe alahb kpee ma woomo ekpabingi ji li sennge edi njom kak. 
\p  
\v 39 Eji ane kpee nyehne ejum jia, bo gbo noongo go ndi, fere rabe re, <<Jehova ye wo li Esowo! Jehova ye wo li Esowo!>> 
\p  
\v 40 Owo Elayija kehm kake bo elkahn re, <<Boben abanyehnamahr ba Baal. Kana taame nne awohng awohng be for!>> Bo kehm bobo bo, Elayija kehm rodo bo tahm go Edamme ji Kison, song wul bo o. 
\p  
\v 41 Owo Elayija kehm tongo ntul Ehab re, <<Song, wo song li, fere wo, tib n kpꞌwuku ewahl egburu elahb.>>  
\v 42 Ano wo Ehab tahme no song li fere wꞌwo, wo Elayija wahre song rehng go ero ewong Kamel, song ji kohk esamahr go ndi ege alahng abal abal. 
\p  
\v 43 Elayija kehm tongo nlokeltum ewe re, <<Song wo song seenge feere go agburu aya.>> Á kehm tahm, song seenge. 
\p Á kehm bungu re, <<Ejumjum o limm.>> 
\p Nkpel esehma nyi Elayija tong-e re, <<Feere song kpur.>> 
\p  
\v 44 Eji biingi nkpel esehma nyio, nlokeltum kehm bungu re, <<Mmon sꞌsohko ekparesemsem ana ebo nne kpꞌlohngo agburu aya.>> Elayija kehm bungu re, <<Song wo song tong Ehab re, <Kuumu go mmvtv akuungu enya, wo song elwaare, fvfo elahb kehm-a bame tv.> >> 
\p  
\v 45 Tvtv ona, akparesemsem ebnyak go elbung, nfeb kehm bake, egburu elahb kehm bake, Ehab fingi song rehng go Jejireel.  
\v 46 Nsahm nyi Jehova kehm yel Elayija, á kehm gbade abomo enye go ebun, á gbo mbang be akpada akpade rehng Jejireel ka Ehab. 
\c 19  
\s1 Elayija Be tahm Go Ewong Ji Sinayi 
\p  
\v 1 Ehab tongo Jejibel nsol kpee nyi Elayija ma lim, fvfo ana á ma wul abanyehnamahr Baal kpee go ekahngkahng.  
\v 2 Ano wo Jejibel tumu etib tv Elayija re, <<Nong asowo lim bib aname, sahb bˈbib aname , re go ngare ana nyia behna, n nehm wul-a ana a wulu ane bako. 
\p  
\v 3 Elayija kehm kehme elfahle, fere be go esi elkpin ene. Eji á ba rehng go Beeseba ji Juda, á tahme nlokeltum ewe o,  
\v 4 yefono antahng mehl eljen efung abehng asongo go edi erikendi ji li wumwum. Á song rehnge go eti ji bo kpo lung re eti anyol kehm song ji go nnahb enye, kehm kake ero re á kpo. Á bungu re, <<Jehova, nsol nyia ebgbal sehng. Ko elkpin ename; N nehme nob sehnge babnsoo ba nkul.>>  
\v 5 Owo á kehm noongo go nnahb eti, fere gbo ellu. 
\p Nkpelnkpel anyehng enjel kehm ba koor-e, kehm bungu re, <<Mehl ji li nsol.>>  
\v 6 Á kehm keebe nyehn, go ege nkpe esi, abred nya bo bane go akal ngun, a ekpꞌkpuk alahb. Á kehm lehke abred, fere wo lahb, feere eje noongo. 
\p  
\v 7 Enjel nyi Jehova kehm kpe feere ba etoono nkpele, kehm ba koor-e, fere bung re, <<Mehl wo li nsol, tibre eljen nia bahke gbale sehng ka-a.>>  
\v 8 Ano wo á mehle li nsol, fere wo alahb. Nsol nyi á li no ka-e eko, á jen eljen nfung atahl abal a atv atahl abal tete á song rehng go Horeb, Egburu Ewong ji Esowo.  
\v 9 O edi jio á song yele go egohng kang o atv mao. 
\s1 Jehova bungu a Elayija 
\p Jehova kehm bungu a ne re, <<Elayija, a kpo lim jen a?>> 
\p  
\v 10 Á kehm faange re, <<Me n yake elname ka wo ntahngtahng, Jehova Esowo bi ga kpi nsahm. Anebe Isreel ebten nwongo enya, bobwa agudu njom enya, fere wul abanyehnamahr eba go akahngkahng. Me ntahngtahng wo ma sa, wo anv bo kpꞌgare re bo wul-m.>> 
\p  
\v 11 Jehova kehm bungu re, <<Lohng wo song yiimi go ero Egburu ewong, go esamahr bi Jehova, tibre Jehova kpꞌsebe re á sehng o.>> 
\p Owo egburu etahntahn elfeb, kehm lohngo ba wa ewong, yehke abahk atal faade go esamamhr bi Jehova, wo Jehova o elfeb woomem. Eji elfeb ma sehng, ndi agbehke kehm bake, wo Jehova o ndi egbehke woomem.  
\v 12 Eji ndi agbehke ma sehng, agun kehm bake, wo Jehova o agun woomem. Eji agun ma sehng, owo momnaange ellum awˈwa kehm bake.  
\v 13 Eji Elayija wuku ellum, á kehm gbibi ewobo eje bulu esamahr. Owo Elayija kehm wuku ellum ni bungu re, <<Elayija, á kpo lim jen a?>> 
\p  
\v 14 Á kehm faange re, <<Me n yake elname ka wo ntahng tahng Jehova Esowo bi ga kpi nsahm. Anebe Isreel ebten nwongo enya, bobwa agudu njom enya, fere wul abanyehnamahr eba go akahngkahng. Me ntahngtahng wo ma sa, wo anv bo kpꞌgare re bo tob wul-m.>>  
\v 15 Jehova kehm-e tongo re, <<Feere song mbang nyi a lohngo ba, fere song go edi erikendi ji wumwum ji Damaskos. Ngare nyi a lꞌrehng o, wohngo Hajael akehng á jol ntul no Aram.  
\v 16 Tob wohngo Jehu mmona Nimsi akehng, á jol ntula Isreel, go Elisa mmona Safati ji lohng go Abel Mehola á ko nji enya ana nnyehnamahr.  
\v 17 Jehu bahke wulu nne awohng awohng no foro go ekahngkahng bi Hajael, fvfo Elisa bahke wulu nne awohng awohng no foro go ekahngkahng bi Jehu.  
\v 18 Me n kuuru ane atahltahl nkpel elku ebal a ane atahl awubu, bo kpee nnene ka gong kak Baal, jol anyo ebo ka sod nnyo eme.>> 
\s1 Mbang nyi Jehova lungu Elisa 
\p  
\v 19 Elayija mehle o, song nyehne Elisa mmona Safati. Á jo jobo ndi egbe a eltahl a enyam eni, bo kpo jen nnyam ebal ebal, Elisa wo jo toono esꞌkohro enyam ebal bi jo tohng asongo. Elayija kehm song kpir-e, song ro ekpawobo eje bul-e.  
\v 20 Elisa kehm yake efong ebe, be toono Elayija. Elisa kehm bungu re, <<Nong me n song tong nsoo a nnee re me n fio, kehm feere ba toon-a.>> 
\p Elayija kehm faange re, <<Song me. Jenji m ma-a lim? 
\p  
\v 21 Ano wo Elisa feere no we-e a kpeem toono. Á rodo efong ebe, wul. Á ko nsol nyi á jo ko lim eltum lam enyam bio fere rod ka ane bo li. Owo á kehm lohngo jo toono Elayija, fere jol nlokeltum ewe. 
\c 20  
\s1 Ben Hadad Ba Bohko Samaria Ebta 
\p  
\v 1 Ben Hadad ntula Siria kehm kuku nsoja enye kpee ba kono edi ajehng. Eltahl atul awubu atul abal ba jolo a ne, a anyˈya ebo, go amvtv akuungu ebo, á mehle song sennge Samaria kak bohko bo ebta.  
\v 2 Á kehm tumu abatiingetib tv Ehab ntula Isreel go nfam nyio re, <<Fvfo ejum ji a ji Ben Hadad bungu no re,  
\v 3 <Asilva a agul enyahne, nya nyame nya, fvfo atingi akal ebahne a abon ebahne ba bame ba.> >> 
\p  
\v 4 Ntula Isreel kehm faange re, << Ana nsoo ntul ewame ma bung, ejum ajehng ajehng ji n kpi no jˈja ji.>> 
\p  
\v 5 Gaam ji, abatiingetib kehm kpe feere ba bung re, <<Ejum ji a ji Ben Hadad bungu no re: <N tumu re wahn yake asilva a agul, akal ebahne a abon ebahne ka-m.  
\v 6 Wo ngare ana nyia behna, m bahke tumu atubesi abalimeltum ebame, bo bahke ba feede ekpasiki ejahne a ntahk nyi atubesi abalimeltum ebahne. Ejum ajehng ajehng ji kpo sahb koren kor bo bahk-n taare tahm a ji.>>> 
\p  
\v 7 Ntula Isreel kehm lungu anebkul ba ejahbe kpee, kehm tong bo re, <<Nyehnen ana nne noa kpꞌsebe ntong! Eji á tumu etib bade akal ebame a abon ebame, asilva a agul enyame, we n faabem nnyo.>> 
\p  
\v 8 Owo anebkul a ane kpee ba lohng ejahbe jio kehm faange re, <<Ke-e wuungu atung, afi taame tv ji á kpꞌbahbe.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Ano wo á kehm faange abatiingetib ntula Ben Hadad re, <<Tongen nsoo ntul ewame Ben Hadad re, <Nlokeltum ewa bahke limi nsol kpee nyi a gbo mbang bahb, ji ma kpe budu n nehm ma lim.> >> Alokeltum feere etib bio song tong Ben Hadad. 
\p  
\v 10 Owo Ben Hadad kehm kpe tum etib behko tv Ehab re, <<Nong asowo bib aname, sahb bˈbib aname, joare n nehm feenge Samaria kpee, jol ndi nyi bahke sake nfam nyio, nehm kpe gbal nyi bahke ruru adabbo nya nsoja enyame bahke kehnge anyi.>> 
\p  
\v 11 Ntula Isreel kehm faange re, <<Tongen ye re, <Nne no ma je ebta nok ga, kpˈfeere kehnge, ye wo fuumu re a wor nnyo sehnge nne no kpˈtahme ebta.> >> 
\p  
\v 12 Ben Hadad wuku etib bia eji ye a atul bako kpi amahm wo go eboa nkpatahk, á kehm lungu nsoja enye tong bo re, <<Tooben song bohko ebta.>> Ano wo bo toobo no re bo song bohko ebta go nfam nyio. 
\s1 Ehab Sehnge Ben Hadad go ebta 
\p  
\v 13 Owo nnyehnamahr awohng kehm bake goji Ehab ntula Isreel ba tiingi re, <<Ejum ji a ji Jehova bungu no re, <A kpꞌnyehne egburu ellong nsoja nia? M bahke faake bo kak-a go ebo lela, owo a bahke kahne re me wo li Jehova.>>> 
\p  
\v 14 Ehab kehm bahbe re, <<Wo nne awoo Jehova bahk-e koko nok ebta bia? 
\p Nnyehnamahr kehm-e faange re, <<Ejum ji a ji Jehova bungu no re, <Ajangkun atubesi nsoja ba wob elwo ni atubesi nsoja yako, bo ba bahke limi jia.> >> 
\p Á kehm bahbe re, <<Nne awoo bahke bohko ebta.>> 
\p Nnyehnamahr kehm faange re, <<Wo bahke bohko.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Ehab kehm lungu ajangkun atubesi nsoja ba wob go elwo ni atubesi nsoja nyako, ane atahl awubu kunu eltahl ane awubu ane abal. Owo á kehm lungu erik nsoja Isreel nyehko, bo kpee jolo ane atahltahl nkpel elku ebal ane atahl awubu.  
\v 16 Bo mehle eljen ngare nyi efin ma yiimi, ngare nyio Ben Hadad a eltahl atul awubu a atul abal ba kpa njahm a ne jolo go eboa nkpatahk ma wo amahm kpˈbuumu.  
\v 17 Ajangkun atubesi nsoja ba wob elwo ni atubesi nsoja nyako ba gbo mbang lohng tahm. Gana Ben-hadad ebtum nsoja, bo ji ba tong-e re,<<Nsoja kpꞌlohngo go Samaria abake.>>  
\v 18 Á kehm bungu re, <<Lꞌjol re bo ba elkoono seb, boben bo mbir mbir, afi bo ba ebta, kana wul na bo, tob boben bo mbir mbir.  
\v 19 Ajangkun nsoja nya woomo elwo ni atubesi nsoja nyako, kehm lohngo eljen nfam nyio asongo, nsoja jo toono bo go njahm.  
\v 20 No nnea nsoja no Isreel wul nnea nsoja no Aram no a lˈkpir-e. Eji anebe Asiria nyehne ano, bo kehm elbeke, anebe Isreel kehm kehme bo kam. Wo Ben Hadad ntula Aram be for go njahm enyꞌnya, a ellong ane ebe ba kpo fing anyꞌnya.  
\v 21 Ntula Isreel kehm kehme bo kam, fere ga anyꞌnya a amvtv akuungu ebo, fere wul anebe Aram gbalee.  
\v 22 Owo nnyehnamahr kehm bake goji ntula Isreel kehm ba tong-e re, <<Toobo elna nob nob, wo fere kahn ejum ji fuumu re wo lim, ngare ana nyia yabv ntula Aram bahke bake kpe ba nok a na.>>  
\v 23 Wo ngare nyia atubesi abalimeltum ntula Aram me-e tub elle re, <<asowo ebo, li asowo nya awong. Owo wahnge bo tahne sehng-r. Wo e lꞌnok a bo go edi ji li ebal ebal, etingitingi e bahke tahne sehnge bo.  
\v 24 Ejum ji a ji fuumu re wo lim: Yehken atul baa kpee bum go nkpe, wahn fere yehke atubesi nsoja nyako ko nji ebo.  
\v 25 Kpe ko ellong nsoja ana ni a ma tane, wo budu elna jol go nrur ana nyˈnehm o, a amvtv akuungu go nrur, eji e lꞌnok a Isreel go edi ebal ebal. Go etingitingi e bahke tahne sehnge ntula Ben-hadad. Á kehm taame tv bo, fere lim jangjang ana bo tong-e no.  
\v 26 Eji elum behko kpe se, Ben Hadad kehm kuku nsoja Aram, bo kehm tahme song rehng go Afek re bo song nok a anebe Isreel.  
\v 27 Eji bo tob kuu anebe Isreel lohng a bo, ka bo nsol ebta, bo kehm lohngo eljen song kpiri bo. Anebe Isreel bumu edi erekekv ebo songo songo wane a bo, are abon ellong ebul na abal ba, wo ga anebe Aram buulu nkpange kpange edi ndi.  
\v 28 Nne Esowo kehm lohngo ba, ba tong ntula Isreel re, <<Ejum ji a ji Jehova bungu no re, <<Tib eji anebe Aram kpꞌtiri re Jehova li esowo bi awong, á limm esowo bis adamme, m bahke faake nsoja nyia nyi li go nrur kak-a go abo, a bahke fere kahn re me Jehova wo.  
\v 29 Nsoja nyi Isreel a nsoja nyi Aram bumu nsi ebo wane atemtem go nfung esehma, efung bi biingi nfung esehma bo bom ebta anoko atemtem. Anebe Isreel wulu anebe Aram ane atahltahl go eltahl a nkpel elon, go nsoja nyi jo jen go akpade go efung abehng.  
\v 30 Erik nsoja nyehko be song yel go ejahbe Afek, edi ji ekahme buku wul bo, ane atahltahl nkpel atahl ara a nkpel esehma a ane atahl awubu. Fvfo Ben Hadad be song rehng go nfam, song biiri go nkimi go atahng ekpꞌkpa.  
\v 31 Atubesi abalimeltum ebe kehm bungu tong-e re, <<Nyehne, wahr ebwuk re atul ba anebe Isreel kpi ndon gbalee. Nong wahr tahmen goji ntula Isreel, wahr boben abomo nkv anoongo go egahre ebun, fere kpennge alehke go egahre asi. Fundiki á bahke tahre elkpin ena.>>  
\v 32 Bo kehm bobo abomo nkv anoongo go ebo ebun, fere kpennge alehke go ebo asi, kehm mehle tahm goji ntula Isreel song tong-e re, <<Nlokeltum ewa Ben Hadad kpꞌbungu re, <N kpa-a gboongo re, kam-a wul.> >> 
\p Ntul kehm faange re, <<Ye noa kpaka li go elkpina? Ye mmonannee wo.>>  
\v 33 Aneblum baa ko nfaange nyi ntul ana elliingi ni nno, bo tob ware ko alum nyanehm o faange re, <<Ee, mmonanne Ben Hadad!>> 
\p Ntul kehm bungu re <<Song ko-n ye ba.>> Eji Ben Hadad lohngo no ba, Ehab yak-e á wahr yel go ege mmvtv akuungu.  
\v 34 Ben Hadad kehm-e tongo re, <<M bahke feere ajahbe nya nsoo taare nso go ebta ka-a. A bahke ma bum edi are jꞌja go Damaskusi, ana nsoo limi no go Samaria.>> 
\p Ehab kehm bungu re, <<Á lꞌlim ji a kpꞌbungu, m bahk-a yake a feere song mbol mbol.>> Ano wo Ehab ko nwongo a Ben-hadab, fere yake á feere kehnge. 
\s1 Nnyehnamahr Ka Ehab Ebi 
\p  
\v 35 Wo Jehova bungu a nne awohng go ellong abanyehnamhr re, á tong nte we re, <<Ko ebti eba wo rum-m,>> 
\p Wo nne noo tˈten.  
\v 36 Nnyehnamahr noo kehm bungu re, <<Tib eji a ki kpunu Jehova, a lꞌsi tˈtahm a, egabe bahk-a wulu.>> Eji nne noo tahme no, egabe kehm-e nyehne go mbang, soro wul-e.  
\v 37 Nnyehnamahr kehm nyehne nne noko kehm-e tongo re, <<Titi rumem.>> Ano wo nne noo rum-e no, fere lim-e nsol.  
\v 38 Owo nnyehnamahr kehm tahme song yiimi go esi mbang jo sik ntul. Á konngo elne nsol go esamahr eji nnene lꞌki-e liingi.  
\v 39 Ana ntul jo sehng go mbang, nnyehnamahr kehm-e lungu fere bung a ne re, <<Me nlokeltum ewa je go mbuksong ebta, fvfo nne kehm bake go egame ba ka-m nne no bo me-e bob go ebta kehm bungu re, <Baabe nnenlum noa. Á lꞌbe for, bo bahke koko elkpin ena go esi elkpin ene, tohko jol ano a bahke tiki kpi ebahk asilva atahltahl nkpel esehma atahl awubu.>  
\v 40 Eji nlokeltum ewa jo lim eltum je go je ga, nne noo be daade.>> 
\p Ntula Isreel kehm bungu re, <<Ano wo elam eja bahke jolo, wob kimi ebi ka elna antahng.>>  
\v 41 Owo nnyehnamahr awohng kehm foomo lennge abomo nya á konngo go esamahr, fvfo ntula Isreel soro liing-e re a tob li nne no kpo tob nnyehn amahr.  
\v 42 Á kehm tong ntul re, <<Ejum ji a ji Jehova ma bung re, <<Wob yake nne no m me-e yehke re á bahke tiki kpo, yeb for. Fvfo esi elkpin ena bahke tahme go esi elkpin ene, ane eba bahke kpoko tib esi ane ebe.> >>  
\v 43 Ano wo ntula Isreel feere no go ege ekpasiki go Samaria a elmarre go erakatahng. 
\c 21  
\s1 Egbe agreb ji Naboti 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ma kang, ejum jolo bade edi egbe agreb ji Naboti nnea Jejireel. Edi jio jolo go Jejireel, kohlo ekpasiki Ehab ntula Samaria.  
\v 2 Efung abehng Ehab kehm tongo Naboti re, <<Ka-m edi egbe agreb eja, me n ko jo bahm anyane ellehke, eji li kohlo egame ekpasiki. Wahr yaange atem, m bahk-a kake edi egbe agreb ji ga nob, afi lꞌkor-a, m bahk-a kpiki ekun abehng abehng bi fuumu edi jio.>> 
\p  
\v 3 Wo Naboti kehm faange re, <<Jehova kꞌtaame re me n ka-a ejum elehkelkv ji babnsoo ewahre>> 
\p  
\v 4 Ano wo Ehab mehle kehnge a elmarre go erakatahng, tib Naboti ebbung re, <<Me wa nehm ka ejum elehkelkv ji babnsoo ewahre.>> Á song noongo go ege edilnong, sennge esamahr go ekahme, fere ten nsol alehke. 
\p  
\v 5 Nkal ewe Jejibel kehm bake, ba bahb-e re, << Nˈnan a kpˈ guunu? Nꞌnan a ma ten nsol alehke? 
\p  
\v 6 Á kehm faange nkal re, <<Tibre n tongo Naboti ji lohng go Jejireel re, <Gung-m edi egbe agreb eja; afi lꞌfere kor-a, m bahk-a edi egbe agreb jindiki yaange asi.> Wo á tong-m re, <N wa nehm ka edi egbe agreb ejame.> >> 
\p  
\v 7 Jejibel nkal ewe kehm bungu re, <<Ano wo eljini ellimi ena li no ana ntul ka Isreela? Mehl ji wo li nsol! Bel eyebatahng. M bahk-a kake edi egbe agreb ji Naboti ji lohng go Jejireel.>> 
\p  
\v 8 Jejibel kehm nyono awer go mbing nyi Ehab, kak elliingi ene go atahng awer, tum awer nyao tv anebkul a agburu ane ba bo lene ano ejahbe ajehng a Naboti.  
\v 9 Awer nyao Jejibel nyono re, 
\p <<Tiingen ane efung bi njal abade a ero akake, bo fere jehke Naboti go eti ekpunu go ellong ane.  
\v 10 Yehken abi ane abal, bo ji go egea mbuksong, bo yiimi ntianse efahnge go ege esamahr re yebsu Esowo a ntul. Owo bo bahk-e rodo lohng a ne, song tuub-e atal wul.>> 
\p  
\v 11 Ano wo anebkul a agburu ane ba lene go ejahbe ji Naboti lene no, limi ana Jejibel tongo bo re bo lim go awer nya á nyono tv bo.  
\v 12 Bo kehm tiingi njal abade, kehm rodo Naboti jehke go edi ekpunu go ellong ane. 
\p  
\v 13 Akimfahnge atianse na abal kehm bake ba ji go ege esamahr, kehm ba kehme nsol tooro nyi Naboti ma lim go esamahr ane re, <<Naboti ebsu Esowo fere tob su ntul.>> Ano wo bo rod-e no tahm go esi mbang, song tuub-e atal á kpo.  
\v 14 Owo bo kehm tumu etib tv Jejibel re, <<Bobtuubu Naboti atal yebkpo.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Ana Jejibel wuku re Naboti bo me-e tuubu atal wul, á kehm tongo Ehab re, <<Tahm, wo song ko edi egbe agreb ji Naboti ji lohng go Jejireel, ji á ten-a elgungu. Á kpeem li go elkpin, yebkpo.  
\v 16 Eji Ehab wuku re Naboti ebkpo, á kehm tahme re, á song ko edi egbe ji Naboti. 
\p  
\v 17 Owo Jehova kehm tongo Elayija ji lohng go Tisibe re,  
\v 18 <<Song wo song kpiri Ehab ntula Isreel, ye ji jehk go Samaria kpˈfili edi. Anv á li go edi egbe agreb ji Naboti, á fi o re á song ko edi egbe agreb jio fere jol nfono.  
\v 19 Tong-e re, <Ejum ji a ji Jehova ma bung re, <Wobwul nne, fvfo wobfere ba nsol enye kpua?>> Fvfo tob tong-e re, <Ejum ji a ji Jehova ma bung re, Go edi ji ebv lahbe alung ma Naboti, ebv bahke tob lahbe alung ema o, Ee, ma ma!> >> 
\p  
\v 20 Ehab kehm tongo Elayija re, <<Nnekv ewame á ma-m seb ba nyehna! nnekv ewame!>> 
\p Elayija kehm-e faange re, <<M ma-a seb ba nyehn, tibre wobrod elna gungu abꞌbi alimi go esamahr bi Jehova.  
\v 21 <Nyehne, Jehova bungu re, M bahke koko elrannge ba kun-a. M bahke rannge ebangenahb eja, fere wul nnenlum awohng awohng go ebangenahb ji Ehab go Isreel, jolo nju afi nja.  
\v 22 M bahke fake etahk eja ana ji Jeroboam mmona Nebati a etahk ji Baasa mmona Ahija, tibre wo ma melle erakatahng ejame, fere lim Isreel boblim abiafem.> 
\p  
\v 23 <<Bada Jejibel fvfo Jehova bungu re, <Ebv bahke lehke ngubjing nyi Jejibel go nkpe ekahme nyi Jejireel.> 
\p  
\v 24 <<Ebv bahke lehke ekv nne awohng awohng no li ka Ehab no bahke kpoko go atahng nfam, fvfo nruk go ekulugbe bahke lehke agubjing nya ane ba bahke kpoko go elatahk nfam. >> 
\p  
\v 25 <<Nne awohng awohng tikem jol ana Ehab no rodo elne lim abꞌbi go esamahr bi Jehova, ye ji Jejibel nkal ewe jo tehme re á lim abˈbi.  
\v 26 Á jo limi nsol ebi mbang, fere jo jen jo toono alokelom, ana anebe Amor ba Jehova kame bo go esamahr bi anebe Isreel.>> 
\p  
\v 27 Ana Ehab wuku alum nyao, á kehm yare abomo enye, fere rod abomo elkv anoongo bobo, agbajake, jo tib egbokondon. Á sa jo jen a abomo elkv anoongo nyao. 
\p  
\v 28 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Elayija ji lohng go Tisibe re:  
\v 29 Wobnyehn ana Ehab ma rede elne go egame esamahra? Tib eji á ma rede elne, n nehm ko elrannge nia ba egea ngare, m bahke koko ba ka etahk eje, ngare nyi mmon ewe.>> 
\c 22  
\s1 Mikaya Nnyehnamahr Rehke Ehab 
\p  
\v 1 Ejum nnya na era, ebta kpeem gbo anebe Aram a anebe Isreel.  
\v 2 Wo goji kpꞌbiingi nnya era Jehosafati ntula Juda mehle je re á song nyehn ntula Isreel.  
\v 3 Ntula Isreel tongo ane ebe ba jolo atubesi ane re, <<Wahn nehme kahn re Ramoti Giled ji jahre jia, wo ń nehme lim ejum ajehng ajehng ji ḿ bahke koko go abo nya ntula Arama?>>  
\v 4 Owo ntul kehm bahbe Jehosafati re, <<Á bahke jeke a name song nok ebta a anebe Ramoti Gileda?>> 
\p Jehosafati kehm faange ntula Isreel re, <<Me n li ana wo li no, ane ebame li ana ane eba, anyˈnya enyame ana anyˈnya enya.>>  
\v 5 Wo Jehosafati tob kpe bungu tong ntula Isreel re, <<Titi gbo mbang seb elle goji Jehova ana á kpꞌtiri bade ejum jia.>>  
\v 6 Ano wo ntula Isreel kehm kuku abanyehnamahr bo ba kono edi ajehng, ejum aneblum atahltahl, kehm ba bahb bo re, <<Fꞌfuumu re me je ebta, song nok a anebe Ramoti Giled, afi me n kꞌje? 
\p >> Bo kehm-e faange re, <<Song, tib Nsoo Ntul bahke faake kak ntul go ebo.>>  
\v 7 Wo Jehosafati kehm bahbe re, <<Nnyehnamahr no Jehova awohng awohng a limma ye ji e bahk-e bahba?>>  
\v 8 Ehab ntula Isreel kehm faange Jehosafati re, <<Ebsa nne nne awohng ana no e bahke ma bahb Jehova sehng go ege abo, wo ye kpo tehn-m tehn, tib á ka nyꞌnyehn amahr nya nno bada name, ngare anyehng anyehng ebi ebi. Nne noo Mikaya mmona Imla wo.>> 
\p Jehosafati kehm faange ntul re, <<Nong ntul kꞌbung jio ano.>>  
\v 9 Ano wo Ehab ntula Isreel lungu nlokeltum ewe awohng kehm bungu re, <<Song, wo song ko Mikaya mmona Imla ba elwaare.>>  
\v 10 Ehab ntul no Isreel a Jehosafati ntul no Juda, liibi nsol etul, ba ji go ebo nti etul, edi ji bo kpo ruumu arasi go eti mbu ji Samaria, a abanyehnamahr yim no kpꞌnyehne amahr go ebo esamahr tong bo.  
\v 11 Nnyehnamahr awohng no bo kpo lung-e re Jedekaya mmona Kenaana eblim atang akuungu fere kehm tongo Ehab re, <<Ejum ji a ji Jehova bungu no re, <Go atang nyaa, a bahke koko atang nyaa nok a anebe Aram tete bo rannge kpee.> >>  
\v 12 Abanyehnamahr bako kpee jo nyehne amahr mbang mbang anyehng. Bo bungu re, <<Song noken anebe Ramoti Giled, ḿ bahke bele esehnge ebta, tib Jehova bahke faake bo kak wo ntul go ebo.>>  
\v 13 Ntiingi etib no tahme Mikaya lung tongo Mikaya re, <<Nyehno, abanyehnamahr bako kpee, kpꞌbungu nnyo amehng re ntul bahke sehnge ebta. Nong ellum ena wane a ni bo, bung nob nob bada ntul.>>  
\v 14 Wo Mikaya kehm bungu re, <<Eji Jehova li go elkpin, m bahke tongo ntul jio ji Jehova tong-m no ji ji.>>  
\v 15 Eji á ba rehng, ntul kehm-e bahbe re, <<Mikaya, fꞌfuumu re wahr je song nok ebta a anebe Ramoti Giled, afi wahr kꞌje?>> 
\p Á kehm faange re, <<Song noken, á bahke bele esehnge ebta, tib Jehova bahke faake bo kak ntul go ebo.>>  
\v 16 Ntul kehm bungu tong-e re, <<Nkpel ebik nyi m bahk-a limi a tir re a m-e nehm tong ejumjum sehngem etingitingi go mbing nyi Jehova?>>  
\v 17 Owo Mikaya kehm faange re, <<N nyehne Isreel kpꞌjene yele yele yele yannge go awong ana ejoro bi ki kpi mbꞌbaabe, owo Jehova kehm bungu re, <Ane baa ntubesi bo kpimm. Nong nne awohng awohng feere kehnge go etahk go elkoono.>>>  
\v 18 Ehab ntula Isreel kehm tongo Jehosafati re, <<Me wa n tong-m re, á ka nyꞌnyehn amahr nya nno bada name, sehngem ebi ji ji?>>  
\v 19 Mikaya kehm soro asi bung re, <<Fvfo wuk ellum ni Jehova ni á bungu re, <<N nyehne Jehova jehk go ege eti etul a ellong enjel kpee ni ejahbetul yim sennge kak go eboblum a ebobkal.  
\v 20 Wo Jehova kehm bungu re, <Nne awoo bahke song fanne Ehab re á song nok a Ramoti Giled, eji á lˈsong kpo o?> 
\p Egom jehko faange mbang nyehka, agom jehko faange nyehko.  
\v 21 Esꞌkohro, etohko kehm ba yiimi go esamahr bi Jehova kehm bungu re, <M bahke song nehm-e.>  
\v 22 Jehova kehm bahbe re, <Go mbang anyii?> 
\p Á kehm bungu re, <<M bahke lohng tahm fere song jol etohko ji afahnge akiimi go anyo nya abanyehnamahr ebe kpee.> 
\p Jehova kehm bungu re, << Á bahk-e ma nehm, song, wo song lim ano.>  
\v 23 Mikaya kehm gohro bung re, << Ji ma jol ji a. Jehova ebkak etohko ji kpo kiimi afahnge go anyo nya abanyehnamahr eba kpee. Jehova ebka ejehke re, ebꞌbi gbo tub-a.>>  
\v 24 Owo Jedekaya mmona Kenaana kehm tahme song ta Mikaya elkpal go esamahr. Á kehm-e bahbe re, <<Limi renan Etohko ji Jehova kehm-m lohngo sa, ba bung a na?>>  
\v 25 Mikaya kehm faange re, <<Bahke sebe kahn efung bio bi á bahke song biiri go nkimi atahng ekpꞌkpa.>>  
\v 26 Ehab ntula Isreel kehm tongo re, <<Roden Mikaya, wahn tum-e feere goji Amon ye ji kpi ejahbe fili a Joasi ji mmona ntul,  
\v 27 wo fere bung re, <Ejum ji a ji ntul ma bung: Kaken nne noa go ngbekobo, wahn fere ka-e abon abahk ebred a abon alahb, tete n feere kehnge ebta nob nob.> >>  
\v 28 Mikaya kehm bungu re, <<Á lꞌlohko feere kehnge nob nob, lohngo re Jehova ka bung sehng go egame.>> Owo á kehm kpe bung re, <<Bumen alum enyame nob nob, wahn ane kpee!>> 
\s1 Ehab bo wul-e go Ramoti Giled 
\p  
\v 29 Ano wo Ehab ntula Isreel a Jehosafati ntula Juda kehm tahme ebta anoko go Ramoti Giled.  
\v 30 Ntula Isreel kehm tongo Jehosafati re, <<M bahke yele ebta bia, kak nsol nyehka nyehka nyi bo lꞌki-m liingi, wo kak nsol etul enya.>> Ano wo ntula Isreel kehm kake nsol nyehka nyehka nyi bo lꞌki-e liingi, fere mehl tahm ebta. 
\p  
\v 31 Ngare nyia ntul no Aram ebtong atubesi nsoja ba kpo fing amvtv akuungu, eltahl ane awubu ane abal re, <<Kana nok a nne awohng awohng noka, jolo egburu nne afi nne no nse, sehngem ntul no Isreel.>>  
\v 32 Eji atubesi nsoja ba kpo fing amvtv akuungu nyehne Jehosafati, bo tiri re, <<Etingitingi nne noa wo li ntula Isreel.>> Owo bo kehm sennge re bo nok a ne, wo eji Jehosafati rabe no,  
\v 33 atubesi nsoja ba kpo fing amvtv akuungu sebe kahn re ye ntul no Isreel sang, bo rahke, bo we kpeem jo kam. 
\p  
\v 34 Wo nne awohng go ellong nsoja Aram kehm take na ta elban ene sehng song jahm ntula Isreel go nkon kon nyi ekpawobo ebta eje. Ntul kehm tongo nne no jo fing mmvtv akuungu enye re, <<Gahl feere wo yehk-m go emahng ebta. Bo ma-m lim ejum.>>  
\v 35 Efung kohro kohro bo jo noko ebta. Wo ntul sa o woomo go mmvtv akuungu enye go mbuksong nyi anebe Aram. Alung ma jo lohng-e ege elok taame na taame go mmvtv akuungu kpee, fvfo elgung nio á kak elkv kpo.  
\v 36 Ana njul kpꞌbake ellahme, etib kehm lohngo ba go ellong nsoja nyi Isreel, ni bungu re, <<Nne awohng awohng feere go ege ejahbe; nne awohng awohng feere go egea ndi!>> 
\p  
\v 37 Ano wo ntul kpo no bo ko-e ba go Samaria, fere kpa-e kak o.  
\v 38 Bo ru alung go mmvtv akuungu go eto ji li go Samaria <<edi ji asꞌsa kpo wuumu alahb,>> fvfo ebv kehm ba lahbe alung eme, ana ellum ni Jehova bungu no. 
\p  
\v 39 Bada nsol nyehko nyi jolo no ngare nyi Ehab jo fili edi, budu nsol kpee nyi á limi no, ekpasiki ji á si no, fere kak avori go atahng, a ajahbe nya á si akahme sennge kak, bo nyˈnyon kak go nwer aka nya atul ba Isreel.  
\v 40 Ehab kehm kpoko ana babnde ebo. Fvfo Ahajiya ji mmon ewe, wo ko nji etul enye. 
\s1 Jehosafati Ntula Juda 
\p  
\v 41 Jehosafati mmona Asa ba kuumu etul bi Juda, ngare nyi Ehab ma ji etul bi Isreel nnya eni.  
\v 42 Jehosafati kange eltahl a nnya elku eji bo bobo etul bi Isreel, fvfo á fili edi go Jeusalem go eltahl a nnya elon. Nnyehn bo jo lung-e re Ajuba mmona Silhi.  
\v 43 Go ejum ajehng ajehng, á jo toono mbang nyi nde Asa, jol á tikem gbake feere go nkpe. Á limi nsol nyi jolo go nseenge go esamahr bi Jehova. Wo ntahk eblom á ranngem, ane soro asi jo lim ajomjom, fere jo fi insen o.  
\v 44 Jehosafati limi elkoono a ntula Isreel. 
\p  
\v 45 Bada nsol nyehko nyi jolo no ngare nyi Jehosafati jo fili edi, nsol nyi á limi no, a eko ebta ji á tibi no, anv bo nyˈnyon go nwer aka nya atul ba Juda.  
\v 46 Á tob kame aneblum ba jo jen asꞌsa ntahk eblom, bo ji sa no bomo ngare nyi nde Asa jo fili edi.  
\v 47 Ngare nyio ntul awohng awohng jolem go Edom; Ekpeele ntul ji jo fili edi. 
\p  
\v 48 Jehosafati kono asohkkahng gbalee re bo jo ko jen are je go Ofir, jo sol agul, jol nsohkkahng anyehng anyehng tikem lohng eljen, rannge o Ejion Gebe.  
\v 49 Owo Ahajiya mmona Ehab kehm tongo Jehosafati re, <<Nong ane ebame jo fing asohkkahng go aya lim eltum a ane eba, wo Jehosafati taamem.  
\v 50 Owo Jehosafati kehm kpoko bo kpa-e kak go ejahbe ji Devid nde. Fvfo Jehoram mmon ewe wo ko nji etul enye. 
\s1 Ahajiya Ntula Isreel 
\p  
\v 51 Ahajiya mmona Ehab kuumu etul bi Isreel go elku a nnya ebal nyi Jehosafati jo fili Juda, fvfo á fili Isreel go nnya ebal.  
\v 52 Á limi abꞌbi go esamahr bi Jehova, tibre á jo jene go abang nya nde abola nnyehn, go abang nya Jeroboam mmona Nebati, ye ji limi Isreel bo jo lim abiafem.  
\v 53 Á jo loko fere jo jom Baal, fere lim Jehova Esowo bi Isreel bel erakatahng jang jang ana nde limi no.